#: ../../content/applications/essentials.rst:3
msgid "Odoo essentials"
msgstr "Osnove Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:3
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Aktivnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:7
msgid "*Activities* are follow-up tasks tied to a record in an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*Aktivnosti* so naloge za nadaljnje ukrepanje, povezane z zapisom v bazi "
"podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:11
msgid ""
"The icon used to display activities varies, depending on the :ref:`activity "
"type <activities/types>`:"
msgstr ""
"Ikona za prikaz aktivnosti se razlikuje glede na :ref:`vrsto aktivnosti "
"<activities/types>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:14
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(clock)` icon: the default activities icon."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(ura)` ikona: privzeta ikona za aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:15
msgid ":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon: a phone call is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telefon)` ikona: načrtovan je telefonski klic."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:16
msgid ":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)` icon: an email is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(ovojnica)` ikona: načrtovano je e-poštno "
"sporočilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:17
msgid ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`(check)` icon: a \"to-do\" is scheduled."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`(kljukica)` ikona: načrtovana je opravilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:18
msgid ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`(users)` icon: a meeting is scheduled."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`(uporabniki)` ikona: načrtovan je sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:19
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)` icon: a document is scheduled to be "
"uploaded."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(naloži)` ikona: načrtovano je nalaganje "
"dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:20
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`(request signature)` icon: a signature "
"request is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`(zahteva za podpis)` ikona: načrtovana "
"je zahteva za podpis."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:23
msgid "Schedule activities"
msgstr "Načrtovanje aktivnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:25
msgid ""
"Activities can be scheduled on any page of the database that contains "
"a :ref:`chatter <activities/chatter>` thread, :ref:`Kanban view <activities/"
"kanban>`, :ref:`list view <activities/list>`, or :ref:`activities view "
"<activities/activity>` of an application."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti je mogoče načrtovati na kateri koli strani baze podatkov, ki "
"vsebuje :ref:`pogovorno nit <activities/chatter>`, :ref:`pogled Kanban "
"<activities/kanban>`, :ref:`seznamski pogled <activities/list>` ali "
":ref:`pogled aktivnosti <activities/activity>` aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:32
msgid "Chatter"
msgstr "Pogovorna nit"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:34
msgid "Activities can be created from the chatter on any record."
msgstr "Aktivnosti je mogoče ustvariti iz pogovorne niti v katerem koli zapisu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:36
msgid ""
"To schedule a new activity, click the :guilabel:`Activity` button, located "
"at the top of the chatter. In the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up "
"window that appears, :ref:`fill out the Schedule Activity form <activities/"
"form>`."
msgstr ""
"Za načrtovanje nove aktivnosti kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Aktivnost`, ki se "
"nahaja na vrhu pogovorne niti. V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Načrtuj "
"aktivnost`, ki se prikaže, :ref:`izpolnite obrazec za načrtovanje aktivnosti "
"<activities/form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "Activity button in chatter field."
msgstr "Gumb za aktivnost v polju pogovorne niti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:46
msgid "Kanban view"
msgstr "Pogled Kanban"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:48
msgid ""
"Activities can also be created from the :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti je mogoče ustvariti tudi iz pogleda :icon:`oi-view-kanban` "
":guilabel:`(Kanban)`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:50
msgid ""
"To do so, click on the |clock| located at the bottom of an individual record."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da kliknete na |clock|, ki se nahaja na dnu posameznega "
"zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:52
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`+ Schedule An Activity`, then proceed to :ref:`fill out the "
"Schedule Activity form <activities/form>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`+ Načrtuj aktivnost`, nato nadaljujte z "
":ref:`izpolnjevanjem obrazca za načrtovanje aktivnosti <activities/form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "Kanban view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Kanban pogled cevovoda CRM in možnost načrtovanja aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:59
#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:77
msgid ""
"If a record already has a scheduled activity, the |clock| is replaced by the "
"icon that represents the existing scheduled activity. Click on the activity "
"type's icon to schedule another activity."
msgstr ""
"Če ima zapis že načrtovano aktivnost, je |clock| nadomestil z ikono, ki "
"predstavlja obstoječo načrtovano aktivnost. Kliknite na ikono vrste "
"aktivnosti za načrtovanje druge aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:65
msgid "List view"
msgstr "Seznam"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:67
msgid ""
"Activities can also be created from a :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(list)` view."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti je mogoče ustvariti tudi iz pogleda :icon:`oi-view-list` "
":guilabel:`(seznam)`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:69
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Activities` column is hidden, reveal it using "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings adjust)` icon in the far-"
"right of the top row."
msgstr ""
"Če je stolpec :guilabel:`Aktivnosti` skrit, ga razkrijte z uporabo ikone "
":icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(prilagoditev nastavitev)` povsem na "
"desni v zgornji vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:72
msgid ""
"Then, click on the |clock| for the record the activity is being added to, "
"and click :guilabel:`+ Schedule an activity`. Proceed to :ref:`fill out the "
"Schedule Activity form <activities/form>` that appears."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite na |clock| za zapis, kateremu se dodaja aktivnost, in kliknite "
":guilabel:`+ Načrtuj aktivnost`. Nadaljujte z :ref:`izpolnjevanjem obrazca "
"Načrtuj aktivnost <activities/form>`, ki se prikazal."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "List view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Pogled seznama cevovoda CRM in možnost načrtovanja aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:86
msgid "Activity view"
msgstr "Pogled aktivnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:88
msgid ""
"Most applications in Odoo have an *Activity* view available. If available, a "
"|clock| is visible in the top-right corner of the main menu bar, amongst the "
"other view option icons."
msgstr ""
"Večina aplikacij v Odoo ima na voljo pogled *Aktivnosti*. Če je na voljo, je "
"|clock| viden v zgornjem desnem kotu glavne vrstice menija med drugimi "
"ikonami možnosti pogleda."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:91
msgid "To open the activity view, click the |clock|."
msgstr "Za odpiranje pogleda aktivnosti kliknite |clock|."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "Top-right menu with the Activities icon called out."
msgstr "Zgornji desni meni z izpostavljeno ikono Aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:96
msgid ""
"In this view, all the available activities are listed in the columns, while "
"the horizontal entries represent all the individual records."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogledu so vse razpoložljive aktivnosti navedene v stolpcih, medtem ko "
"vodoravni vnosi predstavljajo vse posamezne zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:99
msgid ""
"Activities that appear green have a due date in the future, activities that "
"appear orange are due today, while activities appearing red are overdue."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti, ki so zelene, imajo rok v prihodnosti, aktivnosti, ki so "
"oranžne, zapadejo danes, medtem ko so aktivnosti, ki so rdeče, začele."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:102
msgid ""
"Colored bars in each column represent records for specific activity types, "
"and display a number indicating how many activities are scheduled for that "
"type."
msgstr ""
"Barvne vrstice v vsakem stolpcu predstavljajo zapise za določene vrste "
"aktivnosti in prikazujejo številko, ki označuje, koliko aktivnosti je "
"načrtovanih za to vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:105
msgid ""
"If multiple activity types are scheduled for a record, a number appears in "
"the box, indicating the total number of scheduled activities."
msgstr ""
"Če je za zapis načrtovanih več vrst aktivnosti, se v polju pojavi številka, "
"ki označuje skupno število načrtovanih aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:109
msgid ""
"Activity colors, and their relation to an activity's due date, are "
"consistent throughout Odoo, regardless of the activity type, or the view."
msgstr ""
"Barve aktivnosti in njihova povezava z rokom aktivnosti so dosledne v "
"celotnem Odoo, ne glede na vrsto aktivnosti ali pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:112
msgid ""
"To schedule an activity for a record, hover over the corresponding field. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon, and then :ref:`fill out "
"the Schedule Activity form <activities/form>`."
msgstr ""
"Za načrtovanje aktivnosti za zapis premaknite miško nad ustrezno polje. "
"Kliknite na ikono :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` in nato :ref:`izpolnite "
"obrazec Načrtuj aktivnost <activities/form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid ""
"Activity view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Pogled aktivnosti cevovoda CRM in možnost načrtovanja aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:121
msgid "Schedule Activity form"
msgstr "Obrazec Načrtuj aktivnost"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:123
msgid ""
"Activities can be scheduled from many different places, such as from "
"the :ref:`chatter <activities/chatter>` of a record, or from one of multiple "
"views in an application, when available: the :ref:`Kanban view <activities/"
"kanban>`, :ref:`list view <activities/list>`, or :ref:`activity view "
"<activities/activity>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti je mogoče načrtovati iz mnogih različnih mest, na primer iz "
":ref:`klepeta <activities/chatter>` zapisa ali iz enega od več pogledov v "
"aplikaciji, kjer je na voljo: :ref:`pogled Kanban <activities/kanban>`, "
":ref:`pogled seznama <activities/list>` ali :ref:`pogled aktivnosti "
"<activities/activity>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:128
msgid "First, select an activity type:"
msgstr "Najprej izberite vrsto aktivnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:130
msgid ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`To-Do`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Opravilo`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:131
msgid ":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`Email`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`E-pošta`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:132
msgid ":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`Call`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`Klic`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:133
msgid ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Meeting`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Sestanek`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Do Stuff`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Naredi nekaj`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:135
msgid ":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Document`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Dokument`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:136
msgid ":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Signature`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Podpis`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:137
msgid ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Grant Approval`"
msgstr ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Odobri`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:139
msgid "Then, enter the following information:"
msgstr "Nato vnesite naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:141
msgid ""
"**Summary**: enter a short title for the activity, such as `Discuss "
"Proposal`."
msgstr ""
"**Povzetek**: vnesite kratek naslov dejavnosti, na primer `Razpravljaj o "
"predlogu`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:142
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date`: using the calendar popover, select the activity's "
"deadline."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rok`: s pomočjo pojavnega koledarja izberite rok dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Assigned to`: by default, the current user populates this field. "
"To assign a different user to the activity, select them from the drop-down "
"menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodeljeno`: privzeto se to polje zapolni s trenutnim uporabnikom. "
"Če želite dejavnost dodeliti drugemu uporabniku, ga izberite iz spustnega "
"menija."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:145
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Log a note`: add any additional information for the activity in "
"this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zabeleži opombo`: v to polje dodajte morebitne dodatne "
"informacije za dejavnost."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "View of CRM leads and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Pogled CRM potencialnih strank in možnost razporejanja dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:150
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Save` to schedule the activity, and add the activity to the "
"chatter under :guilabel:`Planned Activities`. Click :guilabel:`Mark Done` to "
"add the details of the activity to the chatter under :guilabel:`Today`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da razporedite dejavnost in jo dodate v "
"klepetalo pod :guilabel:`Načrtovane dejavnosti`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Označi "
"kot končano`, da dodate podrobnosti dejavnosti v klepetalo pod "
":guilabel:`Danes`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:155
msgid "Schedule a meeting"
msgstr "Razporedi sestanek"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:157
msgid ""
"If :icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Meeting` is selected as the activity type, "
"enter the information as instructed above, then click :guilabel:`Schedule`. "
"This opens the user's calendar to add and schedule the activity."
msgstr ""
"Če je kot vrsta dejavnosti izbran :icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Sestanek`, "
"vnesite informacije, kot je navedeno zgoraj, nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Razporedi`. To odpre uporabnikov koledar za dodajanje in "
"razporejanje dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:161
msgid ""
"Click on the desired date and time for the activity, and a :guilabel:`New "
"Event` pop-up window appears. The summary from the *Schedule Activity* pop-"
"up window populates the :guilabel:`Title` field."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na želeni datum in čas za dejavnost in prikaže se pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Nov dogodek`. Povzetek iz pojavnega okna *Razporedi dejavnost* se "
"prenese v polje :guilabel:`Naslov`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:165
msgid ""
"Enter the information in the :guilabel:`New Event` pop-up window, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to schedule it. Once scheduled, the activity "
"is added to the chatter under the :guilabel:`Planned Activities` section."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite informacije v pojavno okno :guilabel:`Nov dogodek`, nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`, da ga razporedite. Ko je razporejena, se "
"dejavnost doda v klepetalo pod razdelek :guilabel:`Načrtovane dejavnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:172
msgid "All scheduled activities"
msgstr "Vse razporejene dejavnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:174
msgid ""
"To view a consolidated list of activities, organized by application, click "
"the |clock| in the header menu, located in the top-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti konsolidiran seznam dejavnosti, organiziran po aplikaciji, "
"kliknite |clock| v meniju glave, ki se nahaja v zgornjem desnem kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:177
msgid ""
"If any activities are scheduled, the number of activities appears in a red "
"bubble on the |clock|."
msgstr ""
"Če so načrtovane kakršne koli dejavnosti, se število dejavnosti prikaže v "
"rdečem mehurčku na |clock|."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:179
msgid ""
"All activities for each application are further divided into subsections, "
"indicating where in the application the activity is to be completed. Each "
"sub-section lists the number of scheduled activities that "
"are :guilabel:`Late`, due :guilabel:`Today`, and scheduled in "
"the :guilabel:`Future`."
msgstr ""
"Vse dejavnosti za vsako aplikacijo so dodatno razdeljene v pododseke, ki "
"označujejo, kje v aplikaciji je treba dejavnost dokončati. Vsak pododsek "
"navaja število načrtovanih dejavnosti, ki so :guilabel:`Zamujene`, "
"predvidene :guilabel:`Danes` in načrtovane v :guilabel:`Prihodnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:185
msgid ""
"In the **Time Off** application, one activity is scheduled to be done in the "
"*All Time Off* requests dashboard, and six activities are scheduled to be "
"done in the *Allocations* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji **Odsotnost** je ena dejavnost načrtovana za izvedbo na "
"nadzorni plošči *Vse zahteve za odsotnost* in šest dejavnosti je načrtovanih "
"za izvedbo na nadzorni plošči *Dodelitve*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:188
msgid ""
"These requests appear in two separate lists in the all activities drop-down "
"menu: one labeled `Time Off` and one labeled `Time Off Allocation`."
msgstr ""
"Te zahteve se pojavijo v dveh ločenih seznamih v spustnem meniju vseh "
"dejavnosti: eden z oznako `Time Off` in eden z oznako `Time Off Allocation`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:0
msgid "The list of activities that is accessed from the main menu bar."
msgstr "Seznam dejavnosti, do katerega dostopate iz glavne menijske vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:195
msgid ""
"The option to :ref:`Request a Document <documents/request>` is available at "
"the bottom of the list of all scheduled activities."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :ref:`Zahtevaj dokument <documents/request>` je na voljo na dnu "
"seznama vseh načrtovanih dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:201
msgid "Activity types"
msgstr "Vrste dejavnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:203
msgid ""
"To view the currently configured types of activities in the database, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Discuss section --> Activities "
"setting --> Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled trenutno konfiguriranih vrst dejavnosti v bazi podatkov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> razdelek Razprave --> nastavitev "
"Dejavnosti --> Vrste dejavnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid ""
"Activity Types button in the Settings application under the Discuss section."
msgstr "Gumb Vrste dejavnosti v aplikaciji Nastavitve pod razdelkom Razprave."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:209
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals the :guilabel:`Activity Types` page, where the existing "
"activity types are found."
msgstr ""
"S tem se prikaže stran :guilabel:`Vrste dejavnosti`, kjer najdete obstoječe "
"vrste dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:212
msgid ""
"Individual applications have a list of *Activity Types* dedicated to that "
"application. For example, to view and edit the activities available for the "
"**CRM** application, go to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne aplikacije imajo seznam *Vrst dejavnosti*, namenjen tej "
"aplikaciji. Na primer, za ogled in urejanje dejavnosti, ki so na voljo za "
"aplikacijo **CRM**, pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija CRM --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Vrste dejavnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "The list of activity types already configured and available."
msgstr "Seznam že konfiguriranih in razpoložljivih vrst dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:220
msgid "Edit activity types"
msgstr "Urejanje vrst dejavnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:222
msgid ""
"To edit an existing :ref:`activity type <activities/types>`, click on the "
"activity type, and the activity type form loads."
msgstr ""
"Za urejanje obstoječe :ref:`vrste dejavnosti <activities/types>` kliknite na "
"vrsto dejavnosti in naloži se obrazec vrste dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:225
msgid ""
"Make any desired changes to the activity type form. The form automatically "
"saves, but it can be saved manually at any time by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save Manually` option, represented by a :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` icon, located in the top-left corner of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu vrste dejavnosti naredite želene spremembe. Obrazec se samodejno "
"shrani, vendar ga lahko ročno shranite kadar koli s klikom na možnost "
":guilabel:`Shrani ročno`, ki jo predstavlja ikona :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` "
":guilabel:`(nalaganje v oblak)`, ki se nahaja v zgornjem levem kotu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:230
msgid "Create new activity types"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novih vrst dejavnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:232
msgid ""
"To create a new :ref:`activity type <activities/types>`, "
"click :guilabel:`New` from the :guilabel:`Activity Types` page, and a blank "
"activity type form loads. Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for the activity type at "
"the top of the form, then enter the following information on the form."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove :ref:`vrste dejavnosti <activities/types>` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo` na strani :guilabel:`Vrste dejavnosti` in naloži se prazen "
"obrazec vrste dejavnosti. Na vrhu obrazca vnesite :guilabel:`Ime` za vrsto "
"dejavnosti, nato pa na obrazec vnesite naslednje informacije."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:237
msgid "Activity Settings section"
msgstr "Razdelek Nastavitve dejavnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: Using the drop-down menu, select an action associated "
"with this new activity type. Some actions trigger specific behaviors after "
"an activity is scheduled, such as:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dejanje`: V spustnem meniju izberite dejanje, povezano s to novo "
"vrsto dejavnosti. Nekatera dejanja sprožijo določena vedenja, ko je "
"dejavnost načrtovana, kot so:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload Document`: If selected, a link to upload a document is "
"automatically added to the planned activity in the chatter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naloži dokument`: Če je izbrano, se načrtovanemu opravilu v "
"pogovornem oknu samodejno doda povezava za nalaganje dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:244
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Call`: If selected, call information is logged in the chatter and "
"displayed on relevant records."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Klic`: Če je izbrano, se informacije o klicu zabeležijo v "
"pogovorni trak in prikažejo na ustreznih zapisih."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Meeting`: If selected, a meeting is created in the chatter and "
"displayed on relevant records."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sestanek`: Če je izbrano, se v pogovornem traku ustvari sestanek "
"in prikaže na ustreznih zapisih."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:248
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Request Signature`: If selected, a link to open a signature "
"request pop-up window is automatically added to the planned activity in the "
"chatter. This requires the Odoo **Sign** application to be installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zahtevaj podpis`: Če je izbrano, se načrtovanemu opravilu v "
"pogovornem oknu samodejno doda povezava za odpiranje pojavnega okna zahteve "
"za podpis. To zahteva nameščeno aplikacijo Odoo **Sign**."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:253
msgid ""
"Available activity types vary based on the installed applications in the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Razpoložljive vrste opravil se razlikujejo glede na nameščene aplikacije v "
"bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Folder`: Select a specific :ref:`folder <documents/folders>` to "
"save a document to. This field **only** appears if :guilabel:`Upload "
"Document` is selected for the :guilabel:`Action`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mapa`: Izberite določeno :ref:`mapo <documents/folders>`, v "
"katero želite shraniti dokument. To polje se prikaže **samo**, če je za "
":guilabel:`Dejanje` izbrano :guilabel:`Naloži dokument`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:258
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default User`: Select a user from the drop-down menu to "
"automatically assign this activity to the selected user when this activity "
"type is scheduled. If this field is left blank, the activity is assigned to "
"the user who creates the activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeti uporabnik`: V spustnem meniju izberite uporabnika, ki mu "
"bo to opravilo samodejno dodeljeno, ko je ta vrsta opravila načrtovana. Če "
"to polje ostane prazno, se opravilo dodeli uporabniku, ki opravilo ustvari."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:261
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Summary`: enter a note to include whenever this activity "
"type is created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeti povzetek`: vnesite opombo, ki bo vključena vsakič, ko je "
"ta vrsta opravila ustvarjena."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:264
msgid ""
"The information in the :guilabel:`Default User` and :guilabel:`Default "
"Summary` fields are included when an activity is created. However, they can "
"be altered before the activity is scheduled or saved."
msgstr ""
"Informacije v poljih :guilabel:`Privzeti uporabnik` in :guilabel:`Privzeti "
"povzetek` so vključene, ko je opravilo ustvarjeno. Vendar jih je mogoče "
"spremeniti, preden je opravilo načrtovano ali shranjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:268
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keep Done`: Tick this checkbox to keep activities that have been "
"marked as `Done` visible in the :ref:`activity view <activities/activity>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obdrži opravljeno`: Označite to potrditveno polje, da bodo "
"opravila, ki so označena kot `Opravljeno`, ostala vidna v :ref:`pogledu "
"opravil <activities/activity>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:270
msgid ":guilabel:`Default Note`: enter any notes to appear with the activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeta opomba`: vnesite opombe, ki se bodo prikazale z "
"opravilom."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:273
msgid "Next Activity section"
msgstr "Razdelek naslednje opravilo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:275
msgid ""
"It is possible to have another activity either suggested or triggered. To do "
"so, configure the :guilabel:`Next Activity` section."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je naslednje opravilo predlagati ali sprožiti. Za to konfigurirajte "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Naslednje opravilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:278
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Chaining Type`: select either :guilabel:`Suggest Next Activity` "
"or :guilabel:`Trigger Next Activity` from the drop-down menu. Depending on "
"the selected option, either the :guilabel:`Suggest` or :guilabel:`Trigger` "
"field is displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta veriženja`: v spustnem meniju izberite bodisi "
":guilabel:`Predlagaj naslednje opravilo` bodisi :guilabel:`Sproži naslednje "
"opravilo`. Glede na izbrano možnost se prikaže polje :guilabel:`Predlagaj` "
"ali :guilabel:`Sproži`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:283
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Chaining Type` field does **not** appear if :guilabel:`Upload "
"Document` is selected for the :guilabel:`Action`."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Vrsta veriženja` se **ne** prikaže, če je za "
":guilabel:`Dejanje` izbrano :guilabel:`Naloži dokument`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:286
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggest/Trigger`: depending on what is selected for "
"the :guilabel:`Chaining Type`, this field either "
"displays :guilabel:`Suggest` or :guilabel:`Trigger`. Using the drop-down "
"menu, select the activity to recommend or schedule as a follow-up task to "
"the activity type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Predlagaj/Sproži`: odvisno od tega, kaj je izbrano za "
":guilabel:`Vrsta veriženja`, se v tem polju prikaže :guilabel:`Predlagaj` "
"ali :guilabel:`Sproži`. V spustnem meniju izberite opravilo, ki ga želite "
"priporočiti ali načrtovati kot nadaljnje opravilo vrste opravila."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:289
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: configure when the next activity is suggested or "
"triggered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Načrtuj`: konfigurirajte, kdaj je naslednje opravilo predlagano "
"ali sproženo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:291
msgid ""
"First, enter a numerical value indicating when the activity is suggested or "
"triggered."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite številčno vrednost, ki označuje, kdaj je opravilo predlagano "
"ali sproženo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:293
msgid ""
"Next to this field, a :guilabel:`Days` field is visible. "
"Click :guilabel:`Days`, the default option, to reveal a drop-down menu. "
"Select the desired time-frame option from the list. The options "
"are :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, or :guilabel:`Months`."
msgstr ""
"Ob tem polju je vidno polje :guilabel:`Dnevi`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dnevi`, "
"privzeto možnost, da se prikaže spustni meni. Na seznamu izberite želeni "
"časovni okvir. Možnosti so :guilabel:`Dnevi`, :guilabel:`Tedni` ali "
":guilabel:`Meseci`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:297
msgid ""
"Lastly, using the drop-down menu, select whether the activity is scheduled "
"or triggered either :guilabel:`after previous activity deadline` "
"or :guilabel:`after completion date`."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje v spustnem meniju izberite, ali je opravilo načrtovano ali sproženo "
":guilabel:`po roku prejšnjega opravila` ali :guilabel:`po datumu dokončanja`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "A new Activity form with all the fields filled out."
msgstr "Nov obrazec opravila z vsemi izpolnjenimi polji."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:304
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:305
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss/team_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss/team_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:306
msgid ":doc:`../sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:5
msgid "Contacts"
msgstr "Stiki"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:7
msgid ""
"Contacts are created in the **Contacts** application for customers the "
"company does business with through Odoo. A contact record is a repository of "
"vital business information, facilitating communication and business "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Stiki so ustvarjeni v aplikaciji **Stiki** za stranke, s katerimi podjetje "
"posluje prek Odoo. Zapis stika je shramba bistvenih poslovnih informacij, ki "
"omogoča komunikacijo in poslovne transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:14
msgid "Contact form"
msgstr "Kontaktni obrazec"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:16
msgid ""
"To create a new contact, navigate to the :menuselection:`Contacts app`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. A new form appears where various contact information "
"can be added."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega stika se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Stiki` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Prikaže se nov obrazec, kjer lahko "
"dodate različne kontaktne podatke."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:22
msgid "Contact type"
msgstr "Vrsta stika"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:24
msgid ""
"Odoo supports both :guilabel:`Person` and :guilabel:`Company` contacts. "
"Select the appropriate type for the new contact. Fill in the name of "
"the :guilabel:`Person` or :guilabel:`Company`. This is how the name appears "
"throughout the database. This field is **mandatory**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo podpira stike tipa :guilabel:`Oseba` in :guilabel:`Podjetje`. Izberite "
"ustrezno vrsto za nov stik. Vnesite ime :guilabel:`Osebe` ali "
":guilabel:`Podjetja`. Tako se ime prikazuje v celotni bazi podatkov. To "
"polje je **obvezno**."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Person` contacts can be linked to a :guilabel:`Company` contact. "
"After selecting :guilabel:`Person`, the :guilabel:`Company` field becomes "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"Stike :guilabel:`Oseba` je mogoče povezati s stikom :guilabel:`Podjetje`. Po "
"izbiri :guilabel:`Oseba` postane vidno polje :guilabel:`Podjetje`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)` field, enter the email "
"address with the domain. In the :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)`  field "
"enter the phone number with the appropriate country code. Next, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Address` of the :guilabel:`Company` or :guilabel:`Person`."
msgstr ""
"V polje :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(ovojnica)` vnesite e-poštni naslov z "
"domeno. V polje :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telefon)` vnesite telefonsko "
"številko z ustrezno državno kodo. Nato vnesite :guilabel:`Naslov` "
":guilabel:`Podjetja` ali :guilabel:`Osebe`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:37
msgid "Additional fields"
msgstr "Dodatna polja"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:39
msgid ""
"Additional details are included on the initial form. The following fields "
"are available:"
msgstr ""
"Začetni obrazec vključuje dodatne podrobnosti. Na voljo so naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job Position`: list the job position of the :guilabel:`Person` "
"(only available on :guilabel:`Person`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delovno mesto`: navedite delovno mesto :guilabel:`Osebe` (na "
"voljo samo za :guilabel:`Oseba`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax ID`: the identification number used for tax and accounting "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Davčna številka`: identifikacijska številka, uporabljena za "
"davčne in računovodske namene."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner Level`: select the designated :ref:`partner <contacts/"
"partner-assignment>` level for this contact from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Raven partnerja`: iz spustnega menija izberite določeno "
":ref:`raven partnerja <contacts/partner-assignment>` za ta stik."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: enter the full website address, starting with `http` or "
"`https`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spletna stran`: vnesite celoten spletni naslov, ki se začne s "
"`http` ali `https`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Language`: enter the language used by the contact. All of the "
"emails and documents sent to this contact are then translated to the "
"selected language."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jezik`: vnesite jezik, ki ga uporablja stik. Vsa sporočila in "
"dokumenti, poslani temu stiku, so nato prevedeni v izbrani jezik."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: enter preconfigured tags by typing them in the field, or "
"clicking the drop-down menu, and selecting one. To create a new one, type "
"the new tag in the field, and click :guilabel:`Create` from the resulting "
"drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Značke`: vnesite vnaprej nastavljene značke tako, da jih vtipkate "
"v polje ali kliknete spustni meni in izberete eno. Za ustvarjanje nove "
"vtipkajte novo značko v polje in iz spustnega menija kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:54
msgid "Contacts tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Stiki"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:56
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Contacts` tab, contacts can be added that are associated "
"with a :guilabel:`Company` and related addresses. For example, a specific "
"contact person for the company can be listed here."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Stiki` lahko dodate stike, ki so povezani s "
":guilabel:`Podjetjem` in sorodnimi naslovi. Tukaj je lahko na primer naveden "
"določen kontaktni sogovornik za podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:60
msgid ""
"Multiple addresses can be added on both :guilabel:`Person` "
"and :guilabel:`Company` contacts. To do so, click :guilabel:`Add Contact` in "
"the :guilabel:`Contacts` tab. Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Create Contact` "
"pop-up form, in which additional addresses can be configured."
msgstr ""
"Več naslovov je mogoče dodati tako pri stikih :guilabel:`Oseba` kot "
":guilabel:`Podjetje`. Za to kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj stik` v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Stiki`. S tem se odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Ustvari stik`, v "
"katerem lahko konfigurirate dodatne naslove."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:None
msgid "Add a contact/address to the contact form."
msgstr "Dodajte stik/naslov v kontaktni obrazec."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:67
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form,  select one of the following "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari stik` izberite eno od naslednjih možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:69
msgid ":guilabel:`Contact`: adds another contact to the existing contact form."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stik`: doda nov stik k obstoječemu kontaktnemu obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice`: adds a specific invoice address to the existing contact "
"form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Račun`: doda poseben naslov za izdajo računa k obstoječemu "
"obrazcu stika."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery`: adds a specific delivery address to the existing "
"contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dostava`: doda poseben naslov za dostavo k obstoječemu obrazcu "
"stika."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other`: adds an alternate address to the existing contact form."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Drugo`: doda nadomestni naslov k obstoječemu obrazcu stika."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:None
msgid "Create a new contact/address on a contact form."
msgstr "Ustvarite nov stik/naslov na kontaktnem obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:77
msgid ""
"Once an option is selected, enter the corresponding contact information that "
"should be used for the specified address type."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete možnost, vnesite ustrezne kontaktne podatke, ki naj se uporabijo "
"za navedeno vrsto naslova."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:80
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`Contact Name`, :guilabel:`Address`, :guilabel:`Email`, "
"along with the :guilabel:`Phone` and/or :guilabel:`Mobile` numbers below."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj dodajte :guilabel:`Ime stika`, :guilabel:`Naslov`, :guilabel:`E-"
"pošta` skupaj s številkami :guilabel:`Telefon` in/ali :guilabel:`Mobilni "
"telefon`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:83
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Job Position`, which appears if the :guilabel:`Contact` "
"address type has been selected. This is similar to the :guilabel:`Person` "
"contact."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Delovno mesto`, ki se prikazuje, če je bila izbrana "
"vrsta naslova :guilabel:`Stik`. To je podobno stiku :guilabel:`Oseba`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:86
msgid ""
"To add a note, click on the text field next to :guilabel:`Notes`, and write "
"anything that is applicable to the customer or contact."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje opombe kliknite besedilno polje poleg :guilabel:`Opombe` in "
"napišite karkoli, kar je pomembno za stranko ali stik."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:89
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to save the address, and close "
"the :guilabel:`Create Contact` window. Or, click :guilabel:`Save & New` to "
"save the address, and immediately input another one."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`, da shranite naslov in zaprete "
"okno :guilabel:`Ustvari stik`. Lahko pa kliknete :guilabel:`Shrani in nov`, "
"da shranite naslov in takoj vnesete novega."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:93
msgid "Sales & Purchase tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Prodaja in nakup"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:95
msgid ""
"Next, is the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchases` tab, which only appears when the "
"*Sales*, *Purchase*, **or** *Point of Sale* applications are installed."
msgstr ""
"Sledi zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup`, ki se prikaže samo, če so "
"nameščene aplikacije *Prodaja*, *Nakup* **ali** *Prodajna točka*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:98
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` can be set on the :guilabel:`Sales & "
"Purchases` tab. Select a :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Davčni položaj` se lahko nastavi na zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in "
"nakup`. Izberite :guilabel:`Davčni položaj` iz spustnega menija."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:104
msgid "Sales section"
msgstr "Razdelek Prodaja"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:106
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sales` heading, a specific :guilabel:`Salesperson` can "
"be assigned to a contact. To do that, click the :guilabel:`Salesperson` drop-"
"down field, and select one. Create a new :guilabel:`Salesperson` by typing "
"the user's name, and making the appropriate selection."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Prodaja` je stiku mogoče dodeliti določenega "
":guilabel:`Prodajalca`. To storite tako, da kliknete spustno polje "
":guilabel:`Prodajalec` in izberete enega. Ustvarite novega "
":guilabel:`Prodajalca` tako, da vtipkate uporabniško ime in opravite "
"ustrezno izbiro."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:110
msgid ""
"Certain :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, or a certain :guilabel:`Pricelist`, can "
"also be set, if needed. Click the drop-down menu next to :guilabel:`Payment "
"Terms`, and change it to one of the preselected :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, "
"or :guilabel:`Create` a new one. Select the :guilabel:`Pricelist` drop-down "
"menu to choose the appropriate :guilabel:`Pricelist`."
msgstr ""
"Določeni :guilabel:`Plačilni pogoji` ali določen :guilabel:`Cenik` se lahko "
"nastavijo, če je potrebno. Kliknite spustni meni poleg :guilabel:`Plačilni "
"pogoji` in ga spremenite v enega od vnaprej izbranih :guilabel:`Plačilnih "
"pogojev` ali :guilabel:`Ustvarite` novega. Izberite spustni meni "
":guilabel:`Cenik`, da izberete ustrezen :guilabel:`Cenik`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:115
msgid ""
"Click into the :guilabel:`Delivery Method` field to select an option from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite v polje :guilabel:`Način dostave`, da izberete možnost iz spustnega "
"menija."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:118
msgid "Point Of Sale section"
msgstr "Razdelek prodajna točka"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:120
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Point Of Sale` heading, enter a :guilabel:`Barcode` "
"that can be used to identify the contact."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Prodajna točka` vnesite :guilabel:`Črtno kodo`, ki "
"se lahko uporabi za identifikacijo stika."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:124
msgid "Purchase section"
msgstr "Razdelek nabava"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:126
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Purchase` heading, select how :abbr:`RFQs (requests for "
"quotation)` for this contact should be grouped together:"
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Nabava` izberite, kako naj se :abbr:`povpraševanja "
"za ponudbe` za ta stik združujejo skupaj:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Order`: replenishment needs are grouped together except "
"for :abbr:`MTO (made to order)`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pri naročilu`: potrebe po dopolnitvi so združene skupaj, razen za "
":abbr:`naročilo na zahtevo`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Daily`: replenishment needs are grouped if the expected arrival "
"is the same day."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevno`: potrebe po dopolnitvi so združene, če je pričakovani "
"prihod isti dan."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Weekly`: replenishment needs are grouped if the expected arrival "
"is the same week or week day."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tedensko`: potrebe po dopolnitvi so združene, če je pričakovani "
"prihod isti teden ali dan v tednu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Always`: replenishment needs are always grouped."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vedno`: potrebe po dopolnitvi so vedno združene."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:136
msgid ""
"Select a default :guilabel:`Buyer` if the :abbr:`RFQs (requests for "
"quotation)` should always be assigned to the same user."
msgstr ""
"Izberite privzetega :guilabel:`Kupca`, če naj bodo :abbr:`povpraševanja za "
"ponudbe` vedno dodeljena istemu uporabniku."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:139
msgid ""
"Specify :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, :guilabel:`1099 Box` information, and a "
"preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` here. A :guilabel:`Receipt Reminder` "
"can be set here, as well. Select a :guilabel:`Supplier Currency` to be used "
"for purchases from the contact."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj določite :guilabel:`Plačilni pogoji`, informacije o :guilabel:`Polje "
"1099` in prednostni :guilabel:`Način plačila`. Tukaj je mogoče nastaviti "
"tudi :guilabel:`Opomnik o prejemu`. Izberite :guilabel:`Valuto dobavitelja`, "
"ki se bo uporabljala za nakupe pri tem stiku."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:144
msgid "Fiscal information"
msgstr "Fiskalne informacije"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:146
msgid ""
"To assign a :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` to this contact, select it from the "
"drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Za dodelitev :guilabel:`Fiskalne pozicije` temu stiku jo izberite iz "
"spustnega menija."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:149
msgid "Misc section"
msgstr "Razdelek razno"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:151
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Misc.` heading, enter a :guilabel:`Citizen "
"Identification` number for *Person* contacts, or :guilabel:`Company ID` for "
"*Company* contacts. Use :guilabel:`Reference` field to add any additional "
"information for this contact."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Razno` vnesite številko :guilabel:`Citizen "
"Identification` za stike tipa *Oseba* ali :guilabel:`Company ID` za stike "
"tipa *Podjetje*. Uporabite polje :guilabel:`Reference` za dodajanje dodatnih "
"informacij o tem stiku."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:155
msgid ""
"If this contact should only be accessible for one company in a multi-company "
"database, select it from the :guilabel:`Company` field drop-down list. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Website` drop-down menu to restrict the publishing of this "
"contact to one website (if working on a database with multiple websites)."
msgstr ""
"Če naj bo ta stik dostopen samo za eno podjetje v večpodjetniški zbirki "
"podatkov, ga izberite s spustnega seznama polja :guilabel:`Company`. "
"Uporabite spustni meni :guilabel:`Website`, da omejite objavo tega stika na "
"eno spletno mesto (če delate v zbirki podatkov z več spletnimi mesti)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:160
msgid ""
"Select one or more :guilabel:`Website Tags` to assist in filtering published "
"customers on the `/customers` website page. Select an :guilabel:`Industry` "
"for this contact from the drop-down menu. Use the :guilabel:`SLA Policies` "
"field to assign a *Helpdesk* SLA policy to this contact."
msgstr ""
"Izberite eno ali več :guilabel:`Website Tags`, ki vam bodo pomagale pri "
"filtriranju objavljenih strank na spletni strani `/customers`. V spustnem "
"meniju izberite :guilabel:`Industry` za ta stik. Uporabite polje "
":guilabel:`SLA Policies`, da temu stiku dodelite pravilnik SLA aplikacije "
"*Služba za pomoč*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:165
msgid "Inventory section"
msgstr "Razdelek zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:167
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Inventory` heading, use the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Location` drop-down to select the stock location to be used as a destination "
"when sending goods to this contact. Next, use the :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Location` drop-down to selection the stock location used as a source when "
"recieving goods from this contact. Finally, use the :guilabel:`Subcontractor "
"Location` drop-down to idenfy a location used as both a source and "
"destination when sending goods to this contact during a subcontracting "
"process."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Inventory` uporabite spustni meni "
":guilabel:`Customer Location`, da izberete lokacijo zaloge, ki se bo "
"uporabljala kot cilj pri pošiljanju blaga temu stiku. Nato uporabite spustni "
"meni :guilabel:`Vendor Location`, da izberete lokacijo zaloge, ki se "
"uporablja kot vir pri prejemanju blaga od tega stika. Nazadnje uporabite "
"spustni meni :guilabel:`Subcontractor Location`, da določite lokacijo, ki se "
"uporablja kot vir in cilj pri pošiljanju blaga temu stiku med postopkom "
"podizvajanja."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:175
msgid "Accounting tab"
msgstr "Zavihek računovodstvo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:177
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Accounting` tab appears when the *Accounting* application is "
"installed. Here, a user can add any related :guilabel:`Bank Accounts`, or "
"set default :guilabel:`Accounting entries`."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` se prikaže, ko je nameščena aplikacija "
"*Računovodstvo*. Tukaj lahko uporabnik doda povezane :guilabel:`Bančne "
"račune` ali nastavi privzete :guilabel:`Računovodske vnose`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:180
msgid ""
"Under the :ref:`Invoice Follow-Ups <accounting/follow_up/follow-ups-for-one-"
"customer>` heading, the :guilabel:`Follow-up Status` indicates if the "
"contact currently has any overdue payments. To "
"configure :guilabel:`Reminders` for this contact, use the radio buttons to "
"select either :guilabel:`Automatic` or :guilabel:`Manual` reminders, as well "
"as schedule the :guilabel:`Next Reminder`."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom :ref:`Invoice Follow-Ups <accounting/follow_up/follow-ups-for-"
"one-customer>` polje :guilabel:`Follow-up Status` prikazuje, ali ima stik "
"trenutno kakršna koli zamudna plačila. Za nastavitev :guilabel:`Reminders` "
"za ta stik uporabite izbirne gumbe za izbiro :guilabel:`Automatic` ali "
":guilabel:`Manual` opomnikov ter načrtujte :guilabel:`Next Reminder`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:189
msgid "Partner Assignment tab"
msgstr "Zavihek dodelitev partnerja"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:191
msgid ""
"Next is the :guilabel:`Partner Assignment` tab, which by default, includes "
"a :guilabel:`Geolocation` section, and other partner options, "
"including :guilabel:`Partner Activation` and :guilabel:`Partner Review` "
"configurations. These are **only** present when the *Resellers* module is "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji je zavihek :guilabel:`Dodelitev partnerja`, ki privzeto vključuje "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Geolokacija` in druge možnosti partnerja, vključno z "
"nastavitvami :guilabel:`Aktivacija partnerja` in :guilabel:`Pregled "
"partnerja`. Te so prisotne **samo**, ko je nameščen modul *Prodajalci*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:196
msgid ""
"Follow the :doc:`Resellers documentation <../sales/crm/track_leads/"
"resellers>` for more information on publishing partners on the website."
msgstr ""
"Sledite :doc:`dokumentaciji Prodajalci <../sales/crm/track_leads/resellers>` "
"za več informacij o objavljanju partnerjev na spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:200
msgid "Internal Notes tab"
msgstr "Zavihek interne opombe"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:202
msgid ""
"Following the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab is the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` "
"tab, where notes can be left on this contact form, just like on the contact "
"form noted above."
msgstr ""
"Za zavihkom :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` sledi zavihek :guilabel:`Interne "
"opombe`, kjer je mogoče pustiti opombe na tem obrazcu kontakta, tako kot pri "
"zgoraj omenjenem obrazcu kontakta."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:206
msgid "UBO tab"
msgstr "Zavihek UBO"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:208
msgid ""
"The UBO (Ultimate Beneficial Owner) tab contains a snapshot of the "
"*Holdings* information from the :guilabel:`Equity` app, as well as "
"information for the individual contact, including their :guilabel:`Birth "
"Date` and :guilabel:`Birth Place`."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek UBO (Ultimate Beneficial Owner) vsebuje posnetek informacij o "
"*lastništvu* iz aplikacije :guilabel:`Equity` ter informacije o posameznem "
"stiku, vključno z :guilabel:`Birth Date` in :guilabel:`Birth Place`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:212
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`UBO` tab is **only** present when the *Equity* app is "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`UBO` je prisoten **samo**, ko je nameščena aplikacija "
"*Equity*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:214
msgid ""
"To request the information required for the :abbr:`UBO (Ultimate Beneficial "
"Owner)` tab, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` icon, then "
"select :guilabel:`Request UBO Form` to send an email to the contact."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zahtevati informacije, potrebne za zavihek :abbr:`UBO (Ultimate "
"Beneficial Owner)`, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action`, nato "
"izberite :guilabel:`Request UBO Form`, da stiku pošljete e-poštno sporočilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:219
msgid "Smart buttons"
msgstr "Pametni gumbi"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:221
msgid ""
"At the top of the contact form, there are some additional options available, "
"known as *smart buttons*."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu obrazca kontakta je na voljo nekaj dodatnih možnosti, znanih kot "
"*pametni gumbi*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:224
msgid ""
"Here, Odoo displays a variety of records, related to this contact, that were "
"created on other apps. Odoo integrates information from every single app, so "
"there are many smart buttons."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj Odoo prikazuje različne zapise, povezane s tem kontaktom, ki so bili "
"ustvarjeni v drugih aplikacijah. Odoo integrira informacije iz vsake "
"posamezne aplikacije, zato je pametnih gumbov veliko."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:228
msgid ""
"For example, there is an :guilabel:`Opportunities` smart button, where all "
"the opportunities related to this customer from the *CRM* app are accessible."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, obstaja pametni gumb :guilabel:`Priložnosti`, kjer so dostopne "
"vse priložnosti, povezane s tem kupcem iz aplikacije *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:232
msgid ""
"If the corresponding applications are installed, their related smart buttons "
"appear automatically on a contact form."
msgstr ""
"Če so ustrezne aplikacije nameščene, se njihovi povezani pametni gumbi "
"samodejno prikažejo na obrazcu kontakta."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:235
msgid ""
"A user can see any :guilabel:`Meetings`, :guilabel:`Sales`, :guilabel:`POS "
"Orders`, :guilabel:`Subscriptions`, project :guilabel:`Tasks`, and "
"the :guilabel:`More` smart button reveals additional options, via a drop-"
"down menu. A user can even quickly "
"access :guilabel:`Purchases`, :guilabel:`Helpdesk` tasks, :guilabel:`On-time "
"Rate` for deliveries, :guilabel:`Invoiced` information, :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Bills`, and the :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` connected to this contact."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik lahko vidi :guilabel:`Sestanke`, :guilabel:`Prodajo`, "
":guilabel:`Naročila POS`, :guilabel:`Naročnine`, projektne "
":guilabel:`Naloge` in pametni gumb :guilabel:`Več` razkrije dodatne možnosti "
"prek spustnega menija. Uporabnik lahko celo hitro dostopa do "
":guilabel:`Nakupov`, nalog :guilabel:`Službe za pomoč`, :guilabel:`Stopnje "
"pravočasnosti` za dostave, informacij o :guilabel:`Fakturiranem`, "
":guilabel:`Dobaviteljevih računov` in :guilabel:`Knjige partnerja`, povezane "
"s tem kontaktom."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:241
msgid ""
"Deliveries, documents, loyalty cards, and direct debits are *also* linked to "
"smart buttons, like this, should there be any outstanding/on-file for this "
"contact."
msgstr ""
"Dostave, dokumenti, kartice zvestobe in direktne obremenitve so *prav tako* "
"povezani s pametnimi gumbi, če obstajajo kakšni neporavnani/v evidenci za ta "
"kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:244
msgid ""
"If the contact is a partner, the user can visit their partner page on the "
"Odoo-built website by clicking the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Če je kontakt partner, lahko uporabnik obišče njihovo partnersko stran na "
"spletnem mestu, zgrajenem z Odoo, s klikom na pametni gumb :guilabel:`Pojdi "
"na spletno mesto`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:248
msgid "Archive contacts"
msgstr "Arhiviranje stikov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:250
msgid ""
"If a user decides they no longer want to have this contact active, the "
"record can be archived. To do that, go to the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu at the top of the contact form, and "
"click :guilabel:`Archive`."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabnik odloči, da tega stika ne želi več imeti aktivnega, je mogoče "
"zapis arhivirati. To storite tako, da odprete meni :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanje` na vrhu obrazca stika in kliknete :guilabel:`Arhiviraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:254
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Archive` from the resulting :guilabel:`Confirmation` "
"pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Archive` v pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Confirmation`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:256
msgid ""
"With this contact successfully archived, as indicated by a banner at the "
"top, they do not show up in the main contacts page, but they can still be "
"searched for with the :guilabel:`Archived` filter."
msgstr ""
"Ko je stik uspešno arhiviran, kar nakazuje pasica na vrhu, se ne prikaže več "
"na glavni strani stikov, vendar ga je še vedno mogoče poiskati s filtrom "
":guilabel:`Arhivirano`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:260
msgid ""
"A contact can be *unarchived*, if the user decides to work with them again. "
"To do that, just click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu again at "
"the top of the archived contact form, and click :guilabel:`Unarchive`. Upon "
"doing so, the :guilabel:`Archived` banner is removed, and the contact is "
"restored."
msgstr ""
"Stik je mogoče *razarhivirati*, če uporabnik odloči, da bo z njim znova "
"sodeloval. To storite tako, da znova kliknete meni :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanje` na vrhu obrazca arhiviranega stika in kliknete "
":guilabel:`Razarhiviraj`. S tem se pasica :guilabel:`Arhivirano` odstrani in "
"stik je obnovljen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:266
msgid ""
":doc:`Add different addresses in CRM <../sales/sales/sales_quotations/"
"different_addresses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dodajanje različnih naslovov v CRM <../sales/sales/sales_quotations/"
"different_addresses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:267
msgid ""
"`Odoo's eLearning Contacts tutorial <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"contacts-2527?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Vodnik po stikih v Odoo eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"contacts-2527?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:3
msgid "Merge contacts"
msgstr "Združevanje stikov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's *Contacts* application allows user's to merge duplicate contacts, "
"without losing any information in the process. This keeps the database "
"organized, and prevents contacts from being contacted by more than one "
"salesperson."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija *Stiki* v Odoo omogoča uporabnikom združevanje podvojenih stikov "
"brez izgube informacij. To ohranja podatkovno bazo urejeno in preprečuje, da "
"bi stike kontaktiralo več kot en prodajalec."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:12
msgid "Merge duplicate contacts"
msgstr "Združevanje podvojenih stikov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:15
msgid ""
"Merging is an irreversible action. Do **not** merge contacts unless "
"absolutely certain they should be combined."
msgstr ""
"Združevanje je nepovraten postopek. Stikov **ne** združujte, razen če ste "
"popolnoma prepričani, da jih je treba povezati."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:18
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Contacts app`, and select the :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(list)` icon. Select two or more duplicate contacts from "
"the list, and tick the checkbox (on the far-left) for the contacts that "
"should be merged. Then, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon, "
"and select :guilabel:`Merge` from the resulting drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Odprite aplikacijo :menuselection:`Stiki` in izberite ikono :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(seznam)`. Na seznamu izberite dva ali več podvojenih "
"stikov in označite potrditveno polje (na skrajni levi) za stike, ki jih "
"želite združiti. Nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in v "
"spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`Združi`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:None
msgid "The merge contacts option in the Contacts application."
msgstr "Možnost za združevanje stikov v aplikaciji Stiki."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:27
msgid ""
"This opens the :guilabel:`Merge` pop-up window. From here, review the "
"details of the contacts before confirming they should be merged. If any "
"contacts in the list should **not** be merged, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(delete)` icon at the far right of the contact."
msgstr ""
"To odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Združi`. Tukaj preglejte podrobnosti "
"stikov, preden potrdite, da jih je treba združiti. Če katerega od stikov na "
"seznamu **ne** bi smeli združiti, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`"
"(izbriši)` na skrajni desni strani stika."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:32
msgid ""
"Click the individual contact to open the record for that contact, and view "
"additional information."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite posamezen stik, da odprete zapis za ta stik in si ogledate dodatne "
"informacije."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:None
msgid "The merge pop-up window in the Contacts application."
msgstr "Pojavno okno za združevanje v aplikaciji Stiki."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:39
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Destination Contact` field, and select an option from "
"the drop-down list. This field defaults to the contact record that was "
"created first in the system."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje :guilabel:`Ciljni stik` in na spustnem seznamu izberite "
"možnost. To polje je privzeto nastavljeno na zapis stika, ki je bil v "
"sistemu ustvarjen prvi."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:42
msgid ""
"After confirming the information on the pop-up window, "
"click :guilabel:`Merge Contacts`."
msgstr ""
"Ko potrdite informacije v pojavnem oknu, kliknite :guilabel:`Združi stike`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:45
msgid "Deduplicate contacts"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje podvojenih stikov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:47
msgid ""
"After the merge is finished, a pop-up window appears confirming it is "
"complete. This pop-up window also contains a :guilabel:`Deduplicate the "
"other Contacts` button. This feature searches for duplicated records, based "
"on selected criteria, and merges them automatically, or after manual "
"approval."
msgstr ""
"Ko je združevanje končano, se prikaže pojavno okno, ki potrdi, da je "
"postopek dokončan. To pojavno okno vsebuje tudi gumb :guilabel:`Odstrani "
"podvojene druge stike`. Ta funkcija išče podvojene zapise na podlagi "
"izbranih meril in jih združi samodejno ali po ročni odobritvi."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:52
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Deduplicate the other Contacts` button to open "
"the :guilabel:`Deduplicate Contacts` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Odstrani podvojene druge stike`, da odprete pojavno "
"okno :guilabel:`Odstrani podvojene stike`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:55
msgid ""
"Select one or more fields to be used in the search for duplicated records. "
"Duplicated contacts can be searched, based on the following criteria:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite eno ali več polj, ki bodo uporabljena pri iskanju podvojenih "
"zapisov. Podvojene stike je mogoče iskati na podlagi naslednjih meril:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:58
msgid ":guilabel:`Email`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`E-pošta`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:59
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:60
msgid ":guilabel:`Is Company`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Je podjetje`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`DDV`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:62
msgid ":guilabel:`Parent Company`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Matično podjetje`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:65
msgid ""
"If more than one field is selected, only records that have **all** fields in "
"common are suggested as duplicates."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbranih več polj, so kot podvojeni predlagani samo zapisi, ki imajo "
"**vsa** polja skupna."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:68
msgid ""
"If necessary, select criteria to be used to exclude potential duplicates "
"from the search. Potential duplicates can be excluded from the search, based "
"on the following criteria:"
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi izberite merila, ki bodo uporabljena za izključitev morebitnih "
"podvojenosti iz iskanja. Morebitne podvojenosti je mogoče iz iskanja "
"izključiti na podlagi naslednjih meril:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:71
msgid ":guilabel:`A user associated to the contact`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabnik, povezan s stikom`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal Items associated to the contact`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Postavke dnevnika, povezane s stikom`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:74
msgid ""
"After confirming the search criteria, click either :guilabel:`Merge with "
"Manual Check`, :guilabel:`Merge Automatically`, or :guilabel:`Merge "
"Automatically all process`."
msgstr ""
"Po potrditvi iskalnih meril kliknite :guilabel:`Združi z ročnim "
"preverjanjem`, :guilabel:`Združi samodejno` ali :guilabel:`Samodejno združi "
"celoten proces`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:77
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Merge with Manual Check` is selected, complete the merge by "
"following the :ref:`steps above <contacts/merge-duplicate>`."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete :guilabel:`Združi z ročnim preverjanjem`, dokončajte združevanje "
"po :ref:`zgoraj navedenih korakih <contacts/merge-duplicate>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:3
msgid "Export and import data"
msgstr "Izvoz in uvoz podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo, it is sometimes necessary to export or import data for running "
"reports, or for data modification. This document covers the export and "
"import of data into and out of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo je včasih potrebno izvoziti ali uvoziti podatke za izvajanje poročil "
"ali za spreminjanje podatkov. Ta dokument obravnava izvoz in uvoz podatkov v "
"Odoo in iz njega."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:9
msgid ""
"Sometimes, users run into a 'time out' error, or a record does not process, "
"due to its size. This can occur with large exports, or in cases where the "
"import file is too large. To circumvent this limitation surrounding the size "
"of the records, process exports or imports in smaller batches."
msgstr ""
"Včasih uporabniki naletijo na napako 'časovna omejitev' ali pa se zapis ne "
"obdela zaradi svoje velikosti. To se lahko zgodi pri velikih izvozih ali v "
"primerih, ko je uvozna datoteka prevelika. Da bi se izognili tej omejitvi "
"glede velikosti zapisov, obdelujte izvoz ali uvoz v manjših sklopih."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:16
msgid "Export data from Odoo"
msgstr "Izvoz podatkov iz Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:18
msgid ""
"When working with a database, it is sometimes necessary to export data in a "
"distinct file. Doing so can aid in reporting on activities, although, Odoo "
"provides a precise reporting tool with each available application."
msgstr ""
"Pri delu z bazo podatkov je včasih potrebno izvoziti podatke v ločeno "
"datoteko. To lahko pomaga pri poročanju o aktivnostih, čeprav Odoo "
"zagotavlja natančno orodje za poročanje pri vsaki razpoložljivi aplikaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:22
msgid ""
"With Odoo, the values can be exported from any field in any record. To do "
"so, activate the list view :icon:`fa-list` :guilabel:`(List)` icon, on the "
"items that need to be exported, and then select the records that should be "
"exported. To select a record, tick the checkbox next to the corresponding "
"record. Finally, click the :guilabel:`Action` button, and select :icon:`fa-"
"upload` :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr ""
"Z Odoo je mogoče izvoziti vrednosti iz katerega koli polja v katerem koli "
"zapisu. Za to aktiviraj ikono pogleda seznama :icon:`fa-list` :guilabel:`"
"(Seznam)` pri elementih, ki jih je treba izvoziti, in nato izberi zapise, ki "
"naj bodo izvoženi. Za izbiro zapisa označi potrditveno polje poleg "
"ustreznega zapisa. Nazadnje klikni gumb :guilabel:`Dejanje` in izberi "
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Izvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "View of the different things to enable/click to export data."
msgstr "Prikaz različnih možnosti za omogočanje/klikanje za izvoz podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:31
msgid ""
"When clicking on :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Export`, a :guilabel:`Export "
"Data` pop-over window appears, with several options for the data to export:"
msgstr ""
"Ko klikneš na :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Izvozi`, se prikaže pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Izvozi podatke` z več možnostmi za izvoz podatkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "Overview of options to consider when exporting data in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pregled možnosti, ki jih je treba upoštevati pri izvozu podatkov v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:37
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`I want to update data (import-compatable export)` option "
"ticked, the system only shows the fields that can be imported. This is "
"helpful in the case where the :ref:`existing records need to be updated "
"<essentials/update-data>`. This works like a filter. Leaving the box "
"unticked, gives many more field options because it shows all the fields, not "
"only the ones that can be imported."
msgstr ""
"Z označeno možnostjo :guilabel:`Želim posodobiti podatke (izvoz združljiv z "
"uvozom)` sistem prikaže samo polja, ki jih je mogoče uvoziti. To je "
"koristno, če je treba :ref:`obstoječe zapise posodobiti <essentials/update-"
"data>`. To deluje kot filter. Če pustimo polje neoznačeno, dobimo veliko več "
"možnosti polj, ker prikaže vsa polja, ne samo tistih, ki jih je mogoče "
"uvoziti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:42
msgid ""
"When exporting, there is the option to export in two formats: `.csv` and "
"`.xls`. With `.csv`, items are separated by a comma, while `.xls` holds "
"information about all the worksheets in a file, including both content and "
"formatting."
msgstr ""
"Pri izvozu je na voljo možnost izvoza v dveh formatih: `.csv` in `.xls`. Pri "
"`.csv` so elementi ločeni z vejico, medtem ko `.xls` hrani informacije o "
"vseh delovnih listih v datoteki, vključno z vsebino in oblikovanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:45
msgid ""
"These are the items that can be exported. Use the :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"right` :guilabel:`(Show sub-fields)` icon to display more sub-field options. "
"Use the :guilabel:`Search` bar to find specific fields. To use "
"the :guilabel:`Search` option more efficiently, click on all the :icon:`fa-"
"chevron-right` :guilabel:`(Show sub-fields)` icon to display all fields."
msgstr ""
"To so elementi, ki jih je mogoče izvoziti. Uporabi ikono :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"right` :guilabel:`(Prikaži podpolja)` za prikaz več možnosti podpolj. "
"Uporabi iskalno vrstico :guilabel:`Iskanje` za iskanje določenih polj. Za "
"učinkovitejšo uporabo možnosti :guilabel:`Iskanje` klikni vse ikone "
":icon:`fa-chevron-right` :guilabel:`(Prikaži podpolja)` za prikaz vseh polj."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:49
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(Select field)` icon button is present to add "
"fields to the :guilabel:`Fields to export` list."
msgstr ""
"Gumb z ikono :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(Izberi polje)` je prisoten za "
"dodajanje polj na seznam :guilabel:`Polja za izvoz`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:51
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(Sort)` icon to the left of the selected "
"fields can be used to move the fields up and down, to change the order in "
"which they are displayed in the exported file. Drag-and-drop using "
"the :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(Sort)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(Razvrsti)` levo od izbranih polj se lahko "
"uporabi za premikanje polj gor in dol ter spreminjanje vrstnega reda, v "
"katerem so prikazana v izvoženi datoteki. Povleci in spusti z ikono "
":icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(Razvrsti)`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:54
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Remove field)` icon is used to remove "
"fields. Click the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Remove field)` icon to remove "
"the field."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Odstrani polje)` se uporablja za "
"odstranjevanje polj. Klikni ikono :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Odstrani "
"polje)` za odstranitev polja."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:56
msgid ""
"For recurring reports, it is helpful to save export presets. Select all the "
"needed fields, and click on the template drop-down menu. Once there, click "
"on :guilabel:`New template`, and give a unique name to the export template. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-floppy-o` :guilabel:`(floppy drive)` icon to save the "
"configuration. The next time the same list needs to be exported, select the "
"related template that was previously saved from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Za ponavljajoča se poročila je koristno shraniti predloge izvoza. Izberite "
"vsa potrebna polja in kliknite na spustni meni predlog. Ko ste tam, kliknite "
"na :guilabel:`Nova predloga` in dajte predlogi izvoza edinstveno ime. "
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-floppy-o` :guilabel:`(disketa)`, da shranite "
"konfiguracijo. Naslednjič, ko bo treba izvoziti isti seznam, iz spustnega "
"menija izberite povezano predlogo, ki je bila predhodno shranjena."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:63
msgid ""
"It is helpful to know the field's external identifier. For "
"example, :guilabel:`Related Company` in the export user interface is equal "
"to *parent_id* (external identifier). This is helpful because then, the only "
"data exported is what should be modified and re-imported."
msgstr ""
"Koristno je poznati zunanji identifikator polja. Na primer, "
":guilabel:`Povezano podjetje` v uporabniškem vmesniku za izvoz je enako "
"*parent_id* (zunanji identifikator). To je koristno, ker se nato izvozijo "
"samo podatki, ki jih je treba spremeniti in ponovno uvoziti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:70
msgid "Import data into Odoo"
msgstr "Uvoz podatkov v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:72
msgid ""
"Importing data into Odoo is extremely helpful during implementation, or in "
"times where data needs to be :ref:`updated in bulk <essentials/update-"
"data>`. The following documentation covers how to import data into an Odoo "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz podatkov v Odoo je izjemno uporaben med implementacijo ali kadar je "
"potrebno podatke :ref:`posodobiti množično <essentials/update-data>`. "
"Naslednja dokumentacija zajema, kako uvoziti podatke v podatkovno bazo Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:77
msgid ""
"Imports are permanent and **cannot** be undone. However, it is possible to "
"use filters (`created on` or `last modified`) to identify records changed or "
"created by the import."
msgstr ""
"Uvozi so trajni in jih **ni mogoče** razveljaviti. Vendar je mogoče "
"uporabiti filtre (`ustvarjeno dne` ali `zadnjič spremenjeno`) za "
"prepoznavanje zapisov, ki so bili spremenjeni ali ustvarjeni z uvozom."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:81
msgid ""
"Activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` changes the visible import "
"settings in the left menu. Doing so reveals an :menuselection:`Advanced` "
"menu. Included in this advanced menu are two options: :guilabel:`Track "
"history during import` and :guilabel:`Allow matching with subfields`."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviranje :ref:`razvijalskega načina <developer-mode>` spremeni vidne "
"nastavitve uvoza v levem meniju. S tem se razkrije meni "
":menuselection:`Napredno`. V tem naprednem meniju sta vključeni dve "
"možnosti: :guilabel:`Sledi zgodovini med uvozom` in :guilabel:`Dovoli "
"ujemanje s podpolji`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "Advanced import options when developer mode is activated."
msgstr "Napredne možnosti uvoza, ko je aktiviran razvijalski način."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:88
msgid ""
"If the model uses openchatter, the :guilabel:`Track history during import` "
"option sets up subscriptions and sends notifications during the import, but "
"leads to a slower import."
msgstr ""
"Če model uporablja openchatter, možnost :guilabel:`Sledi zgodovini med "
"uvozom` nastavi naročnine in pošilja obvestila med uvozom, vendar vodi do "
"počasnejšega uvoza."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:91
msgid ""
"Should the :guilabel:`Allow matching with subfields` option be selected, "
"then all subfields within a field are used to match under "
"the :guilabel:`Odoo Field` while importing."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Dovoli ujemanje s podpolji`, se vsa "
"podpolja znotraj polja uporabijo za ujemanje pod :guilabel:`Odoo polje` med "
"uvozom."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:97
msgid "Get started"
msgstr "Uvod"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:99
msgid ""
"Data can be imported on any Odoo business object using either Excel "
"(`.xlsx`) or :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` (`.csv`) formats. This "
"includes: contacts, products, bank statements, journal entries, and orders."
msgstr ""
"Podatke je mogoče uvoziti v kateri koli Odoo poslovni objekt z uporabo "
"formatov Excel (`.xlsx`) ali :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejico)` "
"(`.csv`). To vključuje: stike, izdelke, bančne izpiske, knjižbe in naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:103
msgid ""
"Open the view of the object to which the data should be imported/populated, "
"click on :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Action)` icon, and in the drop-down menu "
"select :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(Import records)`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogled objekta, v katerega naj se podatki uvozijo/vnesejo, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Dejanje)` in v spustnem meniju izberite "
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(Uvozi zapise)`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "Action menu revealed with the import records option highlighted."
msgstr "Meni dejanj z označeno možnostjo uvoza zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:110
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-upload`:guilabel:`Import Template for Customers` at the "
"center of the page to download a :ref:`template <essentials/"
"export_import_data/adapt-a-template>` and populate it with the company's own "
"data. Such templates can be imported in one click since the data mapping is "
"already preconfigured."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-upload`:guilabel:`Uvozi predlogo za stranke` na sredini "
"strani, da prenesete :ref:`predlogo <essentials/export_import_data/adapt-a-"
"template>` in jo napolnite s podatki podjetja. Take predloge je mogoče "
"uvoziti z enim klikom, saj je preslikava podatkov že vnaprej nastavljena."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:115
msgid ""
"To upload the downloaded template or an existing file, follow the next steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za nalaganje prenesene predloge ali obstoječe datoteke sledite naslednjim "
"korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:117
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Upload Data File` and select the desired file."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži podatkovno datoteko` in izberite želeno datoteko."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:118
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Formatting` options as needed (for CSV files only)."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi prilagodite možnosti :guilabel:`Oblikovanje` (samo za datoteke "
"CSV)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:119
msgid ""
"Ensure all data in the :guilabel:`File Column` is correctly mapped to the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Odoo Field` and free of errors."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so vsi podatki v :guilabel:`Stolpcu datoteke` pravilno "
"preslikani v ustrezno :guilabel:`Odoo polje` in brez napak."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:121
msgid ""
"(Optional) Click :guilabel:`Load Data File` to reload the same file or "
"upload a different one."
msgstr ""
"(Neobvezno) Kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži podatkovno datoteko`, da ponovno "
"naložite isto datoteko ali naložite drugo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:122
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Test` to verify that the data is valid."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Test`, da preverite veljavnost podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:123
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Import`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Uvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:126
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Formatting` options do **not** appear when importing the "
"proprietary Excel file type (i.e., `.xls` or `.xlsx`)."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti :guilabel:`Oblikovanje` se **ne** prikažejo pri uvozu lastniške "
"datoteke tipa Excel (tj. `.xls` ali `.xlsx`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:132
msgid "Adapt a template"
msgstr "Prilagodi predlogo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:134
msgid ""
"Import templates are provided in the import tool of the most common data to "
"import (contacts, products, bank statements, etc.). Open them with any "
"spreadsheet software (*Microsoft Office*, *OpenOffice*, *Google Drive*, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Predloge za uvoz so na voljo v orodju za uvoz za najpogostejše podatke za "
"uvoz (stike, izdelke, bančne izpiske itd.). Odprite jih s katerim koli "
"programom za preglednice (*Microsoft Office*, *OpenOffice*, *Google Drive* "
"itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:138
msgid "Once the template is downloaded, proceed to follow these steps:"
msgstr "Ko je predloga prenesena, sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:140
msgid "Add, remove, and sort columns to best fit the data structure."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte, odstranite in razporedite stolpce, da čim bolje ustrezajo strukturi "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:141
msgid ""
"It is strongly advised to **not** remove the :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) "
"column (see why in the next section)."
msgstr ""
"Močno priporočamo, da **ne** odstranite stolpca :guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID) "
"(zakaj, si oglejte v naslednjem razdelku)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:143
msgid ""
"Set a unique ID to every record by dragging down the ID sequencing in "
"the :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) column."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite edinstveni ID za vsak zapis tako, da povlečete navzdol zaporedje "
"ID-jev v stolpcu :guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid ""
"An animation of the mouse dragging down the ID column, so each record has a "
"unique ID."
msgstr ""
"Animacija miške, ki povleče navzdol po stolpcu ID, tako da ima vsak zapis "
"edinstveni ID."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:150
msgid ""
"When a new column is added, Odoo may not be able to map it automatically, if "
"its label does not fit any field within Odoo. However, new columns can be "
"mapped manually when the import is tested. Search the drop-down menu for the "
"corresponding field."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dodan nov stolpec, ga Odoo morda ne bo mogel samodejno preslikati, če "
"njegova oznaka ne ustreza nobenemu polju v Odooju. Nove stolpce pa lahko "
"preslikate ročno med testiranjem uvoza. Poiščite ustrezno polje v spustnem "
"meniju."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "Drop-down menu expanded in the initial import screen on Odoo."
msgstr "Spustni meni razširjen na začetnem zaslonu uvoza v Odooju."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:157
msgid ""
"Then, use this field's label in the import file to ensure future imports are "
"successful."
msgstr ""
"Nato uporabite oznako tega polja v uvozni datoteki, da zagotovite uspešnost "
"prihodnjih uvozov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:160
msgid ""
"Another useful way to find out the proper column names to import is to "
"export a sample file using the fields to be imported. This way, if there is "
"not a sample import template, the names are accurate."
msgstr ""
"Drug uporaben način za ugotavljanje pravilnih imen stolpcev za uvoz je izvoz "
"vzorčne datoteke z uporabo polj, ki jih želite uvoziti. Na ta način, če ni "
"vzorčne predloge za uvoz, so imena točna."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:168
msgid "Import from another application"
msgstr "Uvoz iz druge aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:170
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) is a unique identifier for a line item. It "
"is possible to use an :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) from previous software to "
"facilitate the transition to Odoo."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID) je edinstveni identifikator za postavko vrstice. "
"Mogoče je uporabiti :guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID) iz prejšnje programske "
"opreme, da se olajša prehod na Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:173
msgid ""
"Setting an ID is not mandatory when importing, but it helps in many cases:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev ID-ja pri uvozu ni obvezna, vendar pomaga v številnih primerih:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:175
msgid ""
":ref:`Update imports <essentials/update-data>`: import the same file several "
"times without creating duplicates."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Posodobitev uvozov <essentials/update-data>`: uvozite isto datoteko "
"večkrat, ne da bi ustvarili podvojene zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:177
msgid ":ref:`Import relation fields <export_import_data/relation-fields>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Uvoz relacijskih polj <export_import_data/relation-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:179
msgid ""
"To recreate relationships between different records, the unique identifier "
"from the original application should be used to map it to "
"the :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) column in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za ponovno vzpostavitev povezav med različnimi zapisi uporabite edinstveni "
"identifikator iz prvotne aplikacije in ga preslikajte v stolpec "
":guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID) v Odooju."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:182
msgid ""
"When another record is imported that links to the first one, use **XXX/ID** "
"(XXX/External ID) for the original unique identifier. This record can also "
"be found using its name."
msgstr ""
"Ko je uvožen drug zapis, ki se povezuje s prvim, uporabite **XXX/ID** (XXX/"
"Zunanji ID) za prvotni edinstveni identifikator. Ta zapis lahko najdete tudi "
"z uporabo njegovega imena."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:186
msgid ""
"It should be noted that conflicts occur if two (or more) records have the "
"same *External ID*."
msgstr ""
"Opozoriti je treba, da pride do konfliktov, če imata dva (ali več) zapisi "
"enak *zunanji ID*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:189
msgid "Field missing to map column"
msgstr "Manjkajoče polje za preslikavo stolpca"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:191
msgid ""
"Odoo heuristically tries to find the type of field for each column inside "
"the imported file, based on the first ten lines of the files."
msgstr ""
"Odoo hevristično poskuša ugotoviti vrsto polja za vsak stolpec v uvoženi "
"datoteki na podlagi prvih deset vrstic datoteke."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:194
msgid ""
"For example, if there is a column only containing numbers, only the fields "
"with the *integer* type are presented as options."
msgstr ""
"Če na primer stolpec vsebuje samo števila, so kot možnosti predstavljena "
"samo polja vrste *celo število*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:197
msgid ""
"While this behavior might be beneficial in most cases, it is also possible "
"that it could fail, or the column may be mapped to a field that is not "
"proposed by default."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je to obnašanje v večini primerov koristno, se lahko tudi zgodi, da "
"ne uspe ali da je stolpec preslikan v polje, ki ni privzeto predlagano."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:200
msgid ""
"If this happens, check the :guilabel:`Show fields of relation fields "
"(advanced) option`, then a complete list of fields becomes available for "
"each column."
msgstr ""
"Če se to zgodi, označite možnost :guilabel:`Prikaži polja relacijskih polj "
"(napredno)`, nato pa postane na voljo celoten seznam polj za vsak stolpec."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:None
msgid "Searching for the field to match the tax column."
msgstr "Iskanje polja za ujemanje s stolpcem davka."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:207
msgid "Change data import format"
msgstr "Spremenite obliko zapisa uvoza podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:210
msgid ""
"Odoo can automatically detect if a column is a date, and tries to guess the "
"date format from a set of most commonly used date formats. While this "
"process can work for many date formats, some date formats are not "
"recognizable. This can cause confusion, due to day-month inversions; it is "
"difficult to guess which part of a date format is the day, and which part is "
"the month, in a date, such as `01-03-2016`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo lahko samodejno zazna, ali je stolpec datum, in poskuša uganiti obliko "
"datuma iz nabora najpogosteje uporabljenih oblik datumov. Čeprav ta postopek "
"deluje za številne oblike datumov, nekaterih oblik datumov ni mogoče "
"prepoznati. To lahko povzroči zmedo zaradi inverzije dan-mesec; težko je "
"uganiti, kateri del oblike datuma je dan in kateri del je mesec pri datumu, "
"kot je `01-03-2016`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:216
msgid ""
"When importing a :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file, Odoo "
"provides :guilabel:`Formatting` options."
msgstr ""
"Pri uvozu datoteke :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` Odoo ponuja možnosti "
":guilabel:`Oblikovanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:219
msgid ""
"To view which date format Odoo has found from the file, check "
"the :guilabel:`Date Format` that is shown when clicking on options under the "
"file selector. If this format is incorrect, change it to the preferred "
"format using *ISO 8601* to define the format."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti, katero obliko datuma je Odoo odkril v datoteki, preverite "
":guilabel:`Oblika datuma`, ki je prikazana, ko kliknete na možnosti pod "
"izbirnikom datotek. Če ta oblika ni pravilna, jo spremenite v želeno obliko "
"z uporabo *ISO 8601* za opredelitev oblike."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:224
msgid ""
"*ISO 8601* is an international standard, covering the worldwide exchange, "
"along with the communication of date and time-related data. For example, the "
"date format should be `YYYY-MM-DD`. In the case of July 24th 1981, it should "
"be written as `1981-07-24`."
msgstr ""
"*ISO 8601* je mednarodni standard, ki pokriva svetovni prenos in "
"komunikacijo podatkov, povezanih z datumom in časom. Oblika datuma mora biti "
"na primer `LLLL-MM-DD`. V primeru 24. julija 1981 naj bi bilo zapisano kot "
"`1981-07-24`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:229
msgid ""
"When importing Excel files (`.xls`, `.xlsx`), consider using *date cells* to "
"store dates. This maintains locale date formats for display, regardless of "
"how the date is formatted in Odoo. When importing a :abbr:`CSV (Comma-"
"separated Values)` file, use Odoo's :guilabel:`Formatting` section to select "
"the date format columns to import."
msgstr ""
"Pri uvozu datotek Excel (`.xls`, `.xlsx`) razmislite o uporabi *celic z "
"datumi* za shranjevanje datumov. To ohranja lokalne oblike datumov za "
"prikaz, ne glede na to, kako je datum oblikovan v Odoo. Pri uvozu datoteke "
":abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` uporabite razdelek "
":guilabel:`Oblikovanje` v Odoo za izbiro oblike datuma stolpcev za uvoz."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:235
msgid "Import numbers with currency signs"
msgstr "Uvozite številke z valutnimi simboli"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:237
msgid ""
"Odoo fully supports numbers with parenthesis to represent negative signs, as "
"well as numbers with currency signs attached to them. Odoo also "
"automatically detects which thousand/decimal separator is used. If a "
"currency symbol unknown to Odoo is used, it might not be recognized as a "
"number, and the import crashes."
msgstr ""
"Odoo v celoti podpira številke z oklepaji, ki predstavljajo negativne znake, "
"ter številke z dodanimi valutnimi simboli. Odoo tudi samodejno zazna, kateri "
"ločilnik tisočic/decimalnih mest je uporabljen. Če je uporabljen valutni "
"simbol, ki ga Odoo ne pozna, morda ne bo prepoznan kot številka in uvoz se "
"bo zrušil."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:243
msgid ""
"When importing a :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file, "
"the :guilabel:`Formatting` menu appears on the left-hand column. Under these "
"options, the :guilabel:`Thousands Separator` can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Pri uvozu datoteke :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` se v levem stolpcu "
"prikaže meni :guilabel:`Oblikovanje`. V teh možnostih lahko spremenite "
":guilabel:`Ločilnik tisočic`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:247
msgid ""
"Examples of supported numbers (using 'thirty-two thousand' as the figure):"
msgstr "Primeri podprtih številk (z uporabo 'dvaintrideset tisoč' kot števila):"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:249
msgid "32.000,00"
msgstr "32.000,00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:250
msgid "32000,00"
msgstr "32000,00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:251
msgid "32,000.00"
msgstr "32,000.00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:252
msgid "-32000.00"
msgstr "-32000.00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:253
msgid "(32000.00)"
msgstr "(32000.00)"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:254
msgid "$ 32.000,00"
msgstr "$ 32.000,00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:255
msgid "(32000.00 €)"
msgstr "(32000.00 €)"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:257
msgid "Example that will not work:"
msgstr "Primer, ki ne bo deloval:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:259
msgid "ABC 32.000,00"
msgstr "ABC 32.000,00"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:260
msgid "$ (32.000,00)"
msgstr "$ (32.000,00)"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:263
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`() (parenthesis)` around the number indicates that the number "
"is a negative value. The currency symbol **must** be placed within the "
"parenthesis for Odoo to recognize it as a negative currency value."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`() (oklepaj)` okoli številke označuje, da je številka negativna "
"vrednost. Valutni simbol **mora** biti postavljen znotraj oklepaja, da ga "
"Odoo prepozna kot negativno valutno vrednost."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:268
msgid "Import preview table not displayed correctly"
msgstr "Tabela predogleda uvoza ni pravilno prikazana"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:270
msgid ""
"By default, the import preview is set on commas as field separators, and "
"quotation marks as text delimiters. If the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated "
"Values)` file does not have these settings, modify "
"the :guilabel:`Formatting` options (displayed under "
"the :guilabel:`Import` :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file bar after "
"selecting the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file)."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je predogled uvoza nastavljen na vejice kot ločila polj in "
"narekovaje kot razmejitelje besedila. Če datoteka :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, "
"ločene z vejicami)` nima teh nastavitev, spremenite možnosti "
":guilabel:`Oblikovanje` (prikazane pod vrstico :guilabel:`Uvozi` datoteko "
":abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejicami)` po izbiri datoteke :abbr:`CSV "
"(vrednosti, ločene z vejicami)`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:276
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file has a tabulation as a "
"separator, Odoo does **not** detect the separations. The file format options "
"need to be modified in the spreadsheet application. See the "
"following :ref:`Change CSV file format <export_import_data/change-csv>` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Če ima datoteka :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejicami)` tabulator kot "
"ločilo, Odoo **ne** zazna ločitev. Možnosti oblike datoteke je treba "
"spremeniti v aplikaciji za preglednice. Glejte naslednji razdelek "
":ref:`Spreminjanje oblike datoteke CSV <export_import_data/change-csv>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:284
msgid "Change CSV file format in spreadsheet application"
msgstr "Spreminjanje oblike datoteke CSV v aplikaciji za preglednice"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:286
msgid ""
"When editing and saving :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` files in "
"spreadsheet applications, the computer's regional settings are applied for "
"the separator and delimiter. Odoo suggests using *OpenOffice* or "
"*LibreOffice*, as both applications allow modifications of all three options "
"(from *LibreOffice* application, go to :menuselection:`'Save As' dialog box "
"--> Check the box 'Edit filter settings' --> Save`)."
msgstr ""
"Pri urejanju in shranjevanju datotek :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z "
"vejicami)` v aplikacijah za preglednice se za ločilo in razmejitelj "
"uporabijo regionalne nastavitve računalnika. Odoo predlaga uporabo "
"*OpenOffice* ali *LibreOffice*, saj oba programa omogočata spremembo vseh "
"treh možnosti (iz aplikacije *LibreOffice* pojdite na "
":menuselection:`pogovorno okno 'Shrani kot' --> Označite polje 'Uredi "
"nastavitve filtra' --> Shrani`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:292
msgid ""
"Microsoft Excel can modify the encoding when saving (:menuselection:`'Save "
"As' dialog box --> 'Tools' drop-down menu --> Encoding tab`)."
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Excel lahko spremeni kodiranje pri shranjevanju "
"(:menuselection:`pogovorno okno 'Shrani kot' --> spustni meni 'Orodja' --> "
"zavihek Kodiranje`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:298
msgid "Difference between Database ID and External ID"
msgstr "Razlika med ID-jem baze podatkov in zunanjim ID-jem"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:300
msgid ""
"Some fields define a relationship with another object. For example, the "
"country of a contact is a link to a record of the 'Country' object. When "
"such fields are imported, Odoo has to recreate links between the different "
"records. To help import such fields, Odoo provides three mechanisms."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera polja določajo razmerje z drugim objektom. Na primer, država stika "
"je povezava na zapis objekta 'Država'. Ko se taka polja uvozijo, mora Odoo "
"ponovno ustvariti povezave med različnimi zapisi. Za pomoč pri uvozu takih "
"polj Odoo zagotavlja tri mehanizme."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:305
msgid "**Only one** mechanism should be used per field that is imported."
msgstr "Uporabiti je treba **samo en** mehanizem na polje, ki se uvaža."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:307
msgid ""
"For example, to reference the country of a contact, Odoo proposes three "
"different fields to import:"
msgstr ""
"Na primer, za sklicevanje na državo stika Odoo predlaga tri različna polja "
"za uvoz:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:309
msgid ":guilabel:`Country`: the name or code of the country"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Država`: ime ali koda države"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:310
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country/Database ID`: the unique Odoo ID for a record, defined by "
"the ID PostgreSQL column"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Država/ID baze podatkov`: edinstven ID Odoo za zapis, določen s "
"stolpcem ID PostgreSQL"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:312
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country/External ID`: the ID of this record referenced in another "
"application (or the `.XML` file that imported it)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Država/zunanji ID`: ID tega zapisa, na katerega se sklicuje druga "
"aplikacija (ali datoteka `.XML`, ki ga je uvozila)"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:315
msgid ""
"For the country of Belgium, for example, use one of these three ways to "
"import:"
msgstr ""
"Za državo Belgijo na primer uporabite enega od teh treh načinov za uvoz:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:317
msgid ":guilabel:`Country`: `Belgium`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Država`: `Belgium`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:318
msgid ":guilabel:`Country/Database ID`: `21`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Država/ID baze podatkov`: `21`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:319
msgid ":guilabel:`Country/External ID`: `base.be`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Država/zunanji ID`: `base.be`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:321
msgid ""
"According to the company's need, use one of these three ways to reference "
"records in relations. Here is an example when one or the other should be "
"used, according to the need:"
msgstr ""
"Glede na potrebe podjetja uporabite enega od teh treh načinov za sklicevanje "
"na zapise v razmerjih. Tukaj je primer, kdaj je treba uporabiti enega ali "
"drugega, glede na potrebo:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:324
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`Country`: this is the easiest way when data comes "
"from :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` files that have been created "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :guilabel:`Država`: to je najlažji način, ko podatki prihajajo iz "
"datotek :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejicami)`, ki so bile ustvarjene "
"ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:326
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`Country/Database ID`: this should rarely be used. It is "
"mostly used by developers as the main advantage is to never have conflicts "
"(there may be several records with the same name, but they always have a "
"unique Database ID)"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :guilabel:`Država/ID baze podatkov`: to je treba uporabiti le "
"redko. Večinoma ga uporabljajo razvijalci, saj je glavna prednost, da nikoli "
"ni konfliktov (več zapisov ima lahko enako ime, vendar imajo vedno edinstven "
"ID baze podatkov)"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:329
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`Country/External ID`: use *External ID* when importing data "
"from a third-party application."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :guilabel:`Država/Zunanji ID`: uporabite *Zunanji ID* pri uvozu "
"podatkov iz aplikacije tretje osebe."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:332
msgid ""
"When *External IDs* are used, import :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` "
"files with the :guilabel:`External ID` (ID) column defining the *External "
"ID* of each record that is imported. Then, a reference can be made to that "
"record with columns, like `Field/External ID`. The following two :abbr:`CSV "
"(Comma-separated Values)` files provide an example for products and their "
"categories."
msgstr ""
"Ko se uporabljajo *Zunanji ID-ji*, uvozite :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z "
"vejico)` datoteke s stolpcem :guilabel:`Zunanji ID` (ID), ki določa *Zunanji "
"ID* vsakega zapisa, ki se uvozi. Nato se lahko na ta zapis sklicujete s "
"stolpci, kot je `Polje/Zunanji ID`. Naslednji dve :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, "
"ločene z vejico)` datoteki predstavljata primer izdelkov in njihovih "
"kategorij."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:337
msgid ""
":download:`CSV file for categories <export_import_data/"
"External_id_3rd_party_application_product_categories.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Datoteka CSV za kategorije <export_import_data/"
"External_id_3rd_party_application_product_categories.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:339
msgid ""
":download:`CSV file for Products <export_import_data/"
"External_id_3rd_party_application_products.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Datoteka CSV za izdelke <export_import_data/"
"External_id_3rd_party_application_products.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:345
msgid "Import relation fields"
msgstr "Uvoz relacijskih polj"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:347
msgid ""
"An Odoo object is always related to many other objects (e.g. a product is "
"linked to product categories, attributes, vendors, etc.). To import those "
"relations, the records of the related object need to be imported first, from "
"their own list menu."
msgstr ""
"Objekt Odoo je vedno povezan z mnogimi drugimi objekti (npr. izdelek je "
"povezan s kategorijami izdelkov, atributi, dobavitelji itd.). Za uvoz teh "
"relacij morate najprej uvoziti zapise povezanega objekta iz njihovega menija "
"seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:351
msgid ""
"This can be achieved by using either the name of the related record, or its "
"ID, depending on the circumstances. The ID is expected when two records have "
"the same name. In such a case add `/ ID` at the end of the column title "
"(e.g. for product attributes: `Product Attributes / Attribute / ID`)."
msgstr ""
"To lahko dosežete z uporabo imena povezanega zapisa ali njegovega ID-ja, "
"odvisno od okoliščin. ID se pričakuje, ko imata dva zapisa enako ime. V "
"takem primeru dodajte `/ ID` na konec naslova stolpca (npr. za atribute "
"izdelka: `Atributi izdelka / Atribut / ID`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:356
msgid "Options for multiple matches on fields"
msgstr "Možnosti za več ujemanj pri poljih"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:358
msgid ""
"If, for example, there are two product categories with the child name "
"`Sellable` (e.g. `Misc. Products/Sellable` & `Other Products/Sellable`), the "
"validation is halted, but the data may still be imported. However, Odoo "
"recommends that the data is not imported because it will all be linked to "
"the first `Sellable` category found in the *Product Category* list (`Misc. "
"Products/Sellable`). Odoo, instead, recommends modifying one of the "
"duplicate's values, or the product category hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"Če na primer obstajata dve kategoriji izdelkov z istim imenom podkategorije "
"`Sellable` (npr. `Misc. Products/Sellable` in `Other Products/Sellable`), se "
"preverjanje ustavi, vendar se podatki še vedno lahko uvozijo. Vendar Odoo "
"priporoča, da se podatki ne uvozijo, ker bodo vsi povezani s prvo kategorijo "
"`Sellable`, najdeno na seznamu *Kategorija izdelka* (`Misc. Products/"
"Sellable`). Odoo namesto tega priporoča spremembo ene od podvojenih "
"vrednosti ali hierarhije kategorij izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:365
msgid ""
"However, if the company does not wish to change the configuration of product "
"categories, Odoo recommends making use of the *External ID* for this field, "
"'Category'."
msgstr ""
"Če pa podjetje ne želi spremeniti konfiguracije kategorij izdelkov, Odoo "
"priporoča uporabo *Zunanjega ID-ja* za to polje 'Kategorija'."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:369
msgid "Import many2many relationship fields"
msgstr "Uvoz polj razmerja many2many"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:371
msgid ""
"The tags should be separated by a comma, without any spacing. For example, "
"if a customer needs to be linked to both tags: `Manufacturer` and `Retailer` "
"then 'Manufacturer,Retailer' needs to be encoded in the same column of "
"the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file."
msgstr ""
"Oznake morajo biti ločene z vejico, brez presledkov. Na primer, če je treba "
"stranko povezati z obema oznakama: `Manufacturer` in `Retailer`, je treba v "
"isti stolpec datoteke :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejico)` vpisati "
"'Manufacturer,Retailer'."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:375
msgid ""
":download:`CSV file for Manufacturer, Retailer <export_import_data/m2m-"
"customers-tags.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Datoteka CSV za proizvajalca, trgovca na drobno "
"<export_import_data/m2m-customers-tags.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:378
msgid "Import one2many relationships"
msgstr "Uvoz razmerij one2many"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:380
msgid ""
"If a company wants to import a sales order with several order lines, a "
"specific row **must** be reserved in the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated "
"Values)` file for each order line. The first order line is imported on the "
"same row as the information relative to order. Any additional lines need an "
"additional row that does not have any information in the fields relative to "
"the order."
msgstr ""
"Če želi podjetje uvoziti prodajni nalog z več vrsticami naročila, **mora** "
"biti v datoteki :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejico)` za vsako vrstico "
"naročila rezervirana posebna vrstica. Prva vrstica naročila se uvozi v isto "
"vrstico kot informacije o naročilu. Vse dodatne vrstice potrebujejo dodatno "
"vrstico, ki nima nobenih informacij v poljih, povezanih z naročilom."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:386
msgid ""
"A company imports quotations using a :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` "
"file, based on demo data:"
msgstr ""
"Podjetje uvozi ponudbe z uporabo datoteke :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z "
"vejico)`, ki temelji na predstavitvenih podatkih:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:389
msgid ""
":download:`File for some quotations <export_import_data/o2m-quotations-order-"
"lines.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Datoteka za nekatere ponudbe <export_import_data/o2m-quotations-"
"order-lines.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:391
msgid ""
"A company imports purchase orders with their respective purchase order lines "
"using a :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file:"
msgstr ""
"Podjetje uvozi nabavne naloge z njihovimi nabavnimi vrsticami z uporabo "
"datoteke :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, ločene z vejico)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:394
msgid ""
":download:`Purchase orders with their respective purchase order lines "
"<export_import_data/o2m-purchase-order-lines.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Nabavni nalogi z njihovimi nabavnimi vrsticami "
"<export_import_data/o2m-purchase-order-lines.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:397
msgid ""
"A company imports customers and their respective contacts using a :abbr:`CSV "
"(Comma-separated Values)` file:"
msgstr ""
"Podjetje uvozi stranke in njihove kontakte z uporabo datoteke :abbr:`CSV "
"(vrednosti, ločene z vejico)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:400
msgid ""
":download:`Customers and their respective contacts <export_import_data/o2m-"
"customers-contacts.csv>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Stranke in njihovi kontakti <export_import_data/o2m-customers-"
"contacts.csv>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:405
msgid "Import image files"
msgstr "Uvoz slikovnih datotek"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:407
msgid ""
"To import image files along with the :ref:`uploaded <essentials/"
"export_import_data/get-started>` CSV or Excel file, follow the next steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za uvoz slikovnih datotek skupaj z :ref:`naloženo <essentials/"
"export_import_data/get-started>` datoteko CSV ali Excel sledite naslednjim "
"korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:410
msgid ""
"Add the image file names to the relevant :guilabel:`Image` column in the "
"data file."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte imena slikovnih datotek v ustrezen stolpec :guilabel:`Slika` v "
"podatkovni datoteki."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:411
msgid ""
":ref:`Upload the data file <essentials/export_import_data/get-started>` or "
"reload it by clicking :guilabel:`Load Data File`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Naložite podatkovno datoteko <essentials/export_import_data/get-"
"started>` ali jo znova naložite s klikom na :guilabel:`Naloži podatkovno "
"datoteko`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:413
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your files` under the :guilabel:`Files to import` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži svoje datoteke` pod razdelkom :guilabel:`Datoteke "
"za uvoz`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:414
msgid ""
"Select the relevant image files. The number of files selected appears next "
"to the button."
msgstr ""
"Izberite ustrezne slikovne datoteke. Število izbranih datotek se prikaže "
"poleg gumba."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:415
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Test` to verify that all data is valid."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Test`, da preverite, ali so vsi podatki veljavni."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:416
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Import`. During the import process, Odoo performs a file "
"check to automatically link the uploaded images to the imported data file. "
"If there is no match, the data file is imported without any image."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Import`. Med postopkom uvoza Odoo izvede preverjanje "
"datoteke, da samodejno poveže naložene slike z uvoženo podatkovno datoteko. "
"Če ujemanja ni, se podatkovna datoteka uvozi brez slik."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:422
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Files to import` section is enabled if the product template "
"has an :guilabel:`Image` column with all fields populated."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek :guilabel:`Datoteke za uvoz` je omogočen, če ima predloga izdelka "
"stolpec :guilabel:`Slika` z vsemi izpolnjenimi polji."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:424
msgid ""
"The image file names in the data file must correspond to the uploaded image "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Imena slikovnih datotek v podatkovni datoteki se morajo ujemati z naloženimi "
"slikovnimi datotekami."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:425
msgid ""
"When importing a large number of images, specify the maximum batch size in "
"megabytes and set a delay to prevent the system from becoming overloaded. To "
"do so, :doc:`enable the developer mode <../general/developer_mode>` and fill "
"in the :guilabel:`Max size per batch` and the :guilabel:`Delay after each "
"batch` fields in the :guilabel:`Files to import` section. By default, the "
"delay meets the RPC/API call limit defined in the `Odoo Cloud - Acceptable "
"Use Policy <https://www.odoo.com/acceptable-use>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pri uvozu velikega števila slik navedite največjo velikost paketa v "
"megabajtih in nastavite zamudo, da preprečite preobremenitev sistema. To "
"storite tako, da :doc:`omogočite razvijalski način <../general/"
"developer_mode>` in izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Največja velikost na paket` "
"in :guilabel:`Zamuda po vsakem paketu` v razdelku :guilabel:`Datoteke za "
"uvoz`. Privzeto zamuda ustreza omejitvi klicev RPC/API, določeni v `Odoo "
"Cloud - Pravilnik o sprejemljivi uporabi <https://www.odoo.com/acceptable-"
"use>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:433
msgid "Import records several times"
msgstr "Večkratni uvoz zapisov"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:435
msgid ""
"If an imported file contains one of the columns: :guilabel:`External ID` "
"or :guilabel:`Database ID`, records that have already been imported are "
"modified, instead of being created. This is extremely useful as it allows "
"users to import the same :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file several "
"times, while having made some changes in between two imports."
msgstr ""
"Če uvožena datoteka vsebuje enega od stolpcev: :guilabel:`External ID` ali "
":guilabel:`Database ID`, se že uvoženi zapisi spremenijo namesto da bi se "
"ustvarili novi. To je izjemno uporabno, saj uporabnikom omogoča večkratni "
"uvoz iste datoteke :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` z vmesnimi "
"spremembami med dvema uvozoma."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:440
msgid ""
"Odoo takes care of creating or modifying each record, depending if it is new "
"or not."
msgstr ""
"Odoo poskrbi za ustvarjanje ali spreminjanje vsakega zapisa glede na to, ali "
"je nov ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:442
msgid ""
"This feature allows a company to use the *Import/Export tool* in Odoo to "
"modify a batch of records in a spreadsheet application."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija podjetju omogoča uporabo orodja *Uvoz/Izvoz* v Odoo za "
"spreminjanje skupine zapisov v pregledniški aplikaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:446
msgid "Value not provided for a specific field"
msgstr "Vrednost za določeno polje ni podana"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:448
msgid ""
"If all fields are not set in the CSV file, Odoo assigns the default value "
"for every non-defined field. However, if fields are set with empty values in "
"the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file, Odoo sets the empty value in "
"the field, instead of assigning the default value."
msgstr ""
"Če vsa polja niso nastavljena v datoteki CSV, Odoo dodeli privzeto vrednost "
"za vsako nedoločeno polje. Če pa so polja v datoteki :abbr:`CSV (vrednosti, "
"ločene z vejico)` nastavljena s praznimi vrednostmi, Odoo nastavi prazno "
"vrednost v polje namesto dodelitve privzete vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:453
msgid "Export/import different tables from an SQL application to Odoo"
msgstr "Izvoz/uvoz različnih tabel iz aplikacije SQL v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:455
msgid ""
"If data needs to be imported from different tables, relations need to be "
"recreated between records belonging to different tables. For instance, if "
"companies and people are imported, the link between each person and the "
"company they work for needs to be recreated."
msgstr ""
"Če je treba uvoziti podatke iz različnih tabel, je treba znova vzpostaviti "
"relacije med zapisi, ki pripadajo različnim tabelam. Na primer, če se "
"uvozijo podjetja in osebe, je treba znova vzpostaviti povezavo med vsako "
"osebo in podjetjem, pri katerem dela."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:459
msgid ""
"To manage relations between tables, use the `External ID` facilities of "
"Odoo. The `External ID` of a record is the unique identifier of this record "
"in another application. The `External ID` must be unique across all records "
"of all objects. It is a good practice to prefix this `External ID` with the "
"name of the application or table. (like, 'company_1', 'person_1' - instead "
"of '1')"
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje relacij med tabelami uporabite funkcionalnost `External ID` v "
"Odoo. `External ID` zapisa je edinstveni identifikator tega zapisa v drugi "
"aplikaciji. `External ID` mora biti edinstven za vse zapise vseh objektov. "
"Dobra praksa je, da `External ID` začnete s predpono imena aplikacije ali "
"tabele (npr. 'company_1', 'person_1' – namesto '1')."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:464
msgid ""
"As an example, suppose there is an SQL database with two tables that are to "
"be imported: companies and people. Each person belongs to one company, so "
"the link between a person and the company they work for must be recreated."
msgstr ""
"Predpostavimo, da obstaja podatkovna baza SQL z dvema tabelama, ki ju je "
"treba uvoziti: podjetja in osebe. Vsaka oseba pripada enemu podjetju, zato "
"je treba znova vzpostaviti povezavo med osebo in podjetjem, pri katerem dela."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:468
msgid ""
"Test this example, with a :download:`sample of a PostgreSQL database "
"<export_import_data/database_import_test.sql>`."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusite ta primer z :download:`vzorcem podatkovne baze PostgreSQL "
"<export_import_data/database_import_test.sql>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:471
msgid ""
"First, export all companies and their *External ID*. In PSQL, write the "
"following command:"
msgstr ""
"Najprej izvozite vsa podjetja in njihove *External ID*. V PSQL zapišite "
"naslednji ukaz:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:477
msgid ""
"This SQL command creates the following :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` "
"file:"
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz SQL ustvari naslednjo datoteko :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:486
msgid ""
"To create the :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file for people linked to "
"companies, use the following SQL command in PSQL:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje datoteke :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` za osebe, "
"povezane s podjetji, uporabite naslednji ukaz SQL v PSQL:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:493
msgid "It produces the following :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` file:"
msgstr "To ustvari naslednjo datoteko :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:503
msgid ""
"In this file, Fabien and Laurence are working for the Bigees company "
"(`company_1`), and Eric is working for the Organi company. The relation "
"between people and companies is done using the *External ID* of the "
"companies. The *External ID* is prefixed by the name of the table to avoid a "
"conflict of ID between people and companies (`person_1` and `company_1`, who "
"shared the same ID 1 in the original database)."
msgstr ""
"V tej datoteki Fabien in Laurence delata za podjetje Bigees (`company_1`), "
"Eric pa za podjetje Organi. Relacija med osebami in podjetji je "
"vzpostavljena z uporabo *External ID* podjetij. *External ID* ima predpono "
"imena tabele, da se prepreči konflikt ID med osebami in podjetji (`person_1` "
"in `company_1`, ki sta si delila isti ID 1 v izvirni podatkovni bazi)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:509
msgid ""
"The two files produced are ready to be imported in Odoo without any "
"modifications. After having imported these two :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated "
"Values)` files, there are four contacts and three companies (the first two "
"contacts are linked to the first company). Keep in mind to first import the "
"companies, and then the people."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjeni datoteki sta pripravljeni za uvoz v Odoo brez kakršnih koli "
"sprememb. Po uvozu teh dveh datotek :abbr:`CSV (Comma-separated Values)` "
"boste imeli štiri stike in tri podjetja (prva dva stika sta povezana s prvim "
"podjetjem). Ne pozabite, da morate najprej uvoziti podjetja in nato osebe."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:517
msgid "Update data in Odoo"
msgstr "Posodobitev podatkov v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:519
msgid ""
"Existing data can be updated in bulk through a data import, as long as "
"the :ref:`External ID <essentials/external-id>` remains consistent."
msgstr ""
"Existující data lze hromadně aktualizovat prostřednictvím importu dat, pokud "
"zůstane :ref:`Externí ID <essentials/external-id>` konzistentní."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:523
msgid "Prepare data export"
msgstr "Připravit export dat"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:525
msgid ""
"To update data through an import, first navigate to the data to be updated, "
"and select the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(List)` icon to activate list "
"view. On the far-left side of the list, tick the checkbox for any record to "
"be updated. Then, click :guilabel:`Actions` button, and select :icon:`fa-"
"upload` :guilabel:`Export` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Za posodobitev podatkov prek uvoza najprej poiščite podatke, ki jih želite "
"posodobiti, in izberite ikono :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(Seznam)`, da "
"aktivirate pogled seznama. Na skrajni levi strani seznama označite "
"potrditveno polje za katerikoli zapis, ki ga želite posodobiti. Nato "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Dejanja` in iz spustnega menija izberite :icon:`fa-"
"upload` :guilabel:`Izvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:530
msgid ""
"On the resulting :guilabel:`Export Data` pop-up window, tick the checkbox "
"labeled, :guilabel:`I want to update data (import-compatible export)`. This "
"automatically includes the *External ID* in the export. Additionally, it "
"limits the :guilabel:`Fields to export` list to **only** include fields that "
"are able to be imported."
msgstr ""
"Ve výsledném vyskakovacím okně :guilabel:`Exportovat data` zaškrtněte "
"políčko :guilabel:`Chci aktualizovat data (export kompatibilní s importem)`. "
"Tím se automaticky zahrne *Externí ID* do exportu. Navíc to omezí seznam "
":guilabel:`Pole k exportu` **pouze** na pole, která lze importovat."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:536
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`External ID` field does **not** appear in "
"the :guilabel:`Fields to export` list unless it is manually added, but it is "
"still included in the export. However, if the :guilabel:`I want to update "
"data (import-compatible export)` checkbox is ticked, it is included in the "
"export."
msgstr ""
"Pole :guilabel:`Externí ID` se v seznamu :guilabel:`Pole k exportu` "
"nezobrazí, pokud není přidáno manuálně, ale je stále zahrnuto v exportu. "
"Pokud je však zaškrtnuto políčko :guilabel:`Chci aktualizovat data (export "
"kompatibilní s importem)`, je zahrnuto v exportu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:540
msgid ""
"Select the required fields to be included in the export using "
"the :ref:`options <essentials/export_import_data/export-data>` on the pop-up "
"window, then click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte požadovaná pole, která mají být zahrnuta do exportu, pomocí "
":ref:`možností <essentials/export_import_data/export-data>` ve vyskakovacím "
"okně a poté klikněte na :guilabel:`Exportovat`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:544
msgid "Import updated data"
msgstr "Importovat aktualizovaná data"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:546
msgid ""
"After exporting, make any necessary changes to the data file. When the file "
"is ready, it can be :ref:`imported <essentials/export_import_data/import-"
"data>` by following the same process as a normal data import."
msgstr ""
"Po exportu proveďte v datovém souboru všechny potřebné změny. Když je soubor "
"připraven, může být :ref:`importován <essentials/export_import_data/import-"
"data>` podle stejného postupu jako běžný import dat."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:551
msgid ""
"When updating data, it is extremely important that the *External ID* remain "
"consistent, as this is how the system identifies a record. If an ID is "
"altered, or removed, the system may add a duplicate record, instead of "
"updating the existing one."
msgstr ""
"Při aktualizaci dat je mimořádně důležité, aby *Externí ID* zůstalo "
"konzistentní, protože tímto způsobem systém identifikuje záznam. Pokud je ID "
"změněno nebo odstraněno, systém může místo aktualizace existujícího záznamu "
"přidat duplicitní záznam."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:5
msgid "Odoo rich-text editor"
msgstr "Odoo editor formátovaného textu"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Odoo rich-text editor allows for creating and editing rich-text content "
"in HTML fields, such as the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` "
"and :guilabel:`Description` fields, as well as in the :ref:`Knowledge "
"articles <knowledge/articles_editing/edit-article>` and the :ref:`Studio "
"report editor <studio/pdf-reports/report-editor>`, among others. Start "
"typing or use the :ref:`toolbar <essentials/html_editor/toolbar>` "
"or :ref:`powerbox <essentials/html_editor/commands>` for formatting and "
"structuring text."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik obogatenega besedila Odoo omogoča ustvarjanje in urejanje "
"vsebine obogatenega besedila v poljih HTML, kot sta polji "
":guilabel:`Internal Notes` in :guilabel:`Description`, kot tudi v "
":ref:`Knowledge articles <knowledge/articles_editing/edit-article>` in "
":ref:`Studio report editor <studio/pdf-reports/report-editor>` ter drugih. "
"Začnite tipkati ali uporabite :ref:`toolbar <essentials/html_editor/toolbar>"
"` ali :ref:`powerbox <essentials/html_editor/commands>` za oblikovanje in "
"strukturiranje besedila."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:15
msgid ""
"Hover over any element in the text (header, table, clipboard, etc.) to "
"reveal the :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(drag)` icon. Click and hold the icon "
"to drag and drop the element elsewhere in the text."
msgstr ""
"Přejetím myši přes jakýkoli prvek v textu (nadpis, tabulka, schránka atd.) "
"se zobrazí ikona :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(přesunout)`. Klikněte na ikonu "
"a přetáhněte prvek na jiné místo v textu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:22
msgid "Text editor toolbar"
msgstr "Panel nástrojů textového editoru"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:24
msgid ""
"To edit a word, sentence, or paragraph, select or double-click it to display "
"the text editor toolbar and apply any of the following standard formatting "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti besedo, stavek ali odstavek, ga izberite ali dvokliknite, "
"da se prikaže orodna vrstica urejevalnika besedila, in uporabite katero koli "
"od naslednjih standardnih možnosti oblikovanja:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Font style**: Define the font style using various options, such "
"as :guilabel:`Header 1 to 6, Normal, Paragraph, Code`, and :guilabel:`Quote`."
msgstr ""
"**Slog pisave**: določite slog pisave z različnimi možnostmi, kot so "
":guilabel:`Header 1 to 6, Normal, Paragraph, Code` in :guilabel:`Quote`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:29
msgid "**Font size**: Select the preferred font size."
msgstr "**Velikost pisave**: izberite želeno velikost pisave."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:30
msgid ":icon:`fa-bold` (:guilabel:`Toggle bold`): Put the text in bold."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-bold` (:guilabel:`Toggle bold`): krepko oblikuje besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:31
msgid ":icon:`fa-italic` (:guilabel:`Toggle italic`): Put the text in italics."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-italic` (:guilabel:`Toggle italic`): ležeče oblikuje besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:32
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-underline` (:guilabel:`Toggle underline`): Underline the text."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-underline` (:guilabel:`Toggle underline`): podčrta besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:33
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-font` (:guilabel:`Apply Font Color`): Customize the font colors:"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-font` (:guilabel:`Apply Font Color`): prilagodite barve pisave:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Solid`: Select the preferred color from the predefined palette."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Plná`: Vyberte preferovanou barvu z předdefinované palety."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom`: Customize the color palette using the wheel or by "
"configuring the :guilabel:`hex` code and :guilabel:`RGBA` values."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vlastní`: Přizpůsobte barevnou paletu pomocí kolečka nebo "
"nakonfigurováním :guilabel:`hex` kódu a hodnot :guilabel:`RGBA`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Gradient`: Select a predefined gradient or customize it by "
"choosing between :guilabel:`Linear` or :guilabel:`Radial` and adjusting the "
"wheel."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Přechod`: Vyberte předdefinovaný přechod nebo jej přizpůsobte "
"výběrem mezi :guilabel:`Lineární` nebo :guilabel:`Radiální` a úpravou "
"kolečka."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:40
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`Reset`): Restore the original font/background "
"color."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`Reset`): obnovi izvorno barvo pisave/ozadja."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:42
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`Add a link`): Insert or edit a URL link to a "
"selected text, and optionally upload an image using its file URL."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`Dodaj povezavo`): Vstavite ali uredite URL "
"povezavo k izbranemu besedilu in po želji naložite sliko z uporabo njene URL "
"datoteke."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Odoo AI`: Write a prompt and get AI-generated content. "
"Optionally, click the AI suggestions instead of writing a prompt."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odoo AI`: Napišite poziv in pridobite vsebino, ustvarjeno z AI. "
"Po želji kliknite predloge AI namesto pisanja poziva."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:47
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Expand toolbar`) icon to display "
"additional formatting options:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Razširi orodno vrstico`), "
"da prikažete dodatne možnosti oblikovanja:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:50
msgid ""
"**Font family**: Use the :guilabel:`Default system font` or select a "
"preferred font family for the text."
msgstr ""
"**Družina pisav**: Uporabite :guilabel:`Privzeto sistemsko pisavo` ali "
"izberite želeno družino pisav za besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/html_editor.rst:52
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-strikethrough` (:guilabel:`Toggle strikethrough`): Strike through "
